"housing costs, including rent/mortgage, utilities, and insurance."
msgstr ""
"Garis panduan am adalah untuk membelanjakan tidak lebih daripada 30%% "
"daripada pendapatan kasar anda untuk kos perumahan, termasuk sewa/gadai "
"janji, utiliti dan insurans."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:363
msgid "How do I build an emergency fund?"
msgstr "Bagaimanakah saya membina dana kecemasan?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/budget_calculator.html:369
msgid ""
"Start by saving $1,000, then work toward 3-6 months of expenses. Automate "
"transfers to a separate savings account. Any 'remaining' budget should go "
"here first."
msgstr ""
"Mulakan dengan menyimpan $1,000, kemudian berusaha ke arah perbelanjaan 3-6 "
"bulan. Automatikkan pemindahan ke akaun simpanan yang berasingan. Sebarang "
"bajet 'baki' hendaklah di sini dahulu."

