msgid "Understanding Future Value"
msgstr "Memahami Nilai Masa Depan"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:211
msgid "The Power of Compound Interest"
msgstr "Kuasa Kepentingan Kompaun"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:212
msgid ""
"Compound interest means you earn interest on your interest. The longer your "
"money compounds, the faster it grows. Starting early is the most powerful "
"factor."
msgstr ""
"Faedah kompaun bermakna anda memperoleh faedah atas faedah anda. Semakin "
"lama wang anda berkumpul, semakin cepat ia berkembang. Bermula awal adalah "
"faktor yang paling kuat."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:215
msgid "Regular Contributions Matter"
msgstr "Sumbangan Tetap Penting"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:216
msgid ""
"Consistent monthly contributions can often contribute more to your final "
"balance than your initial investment, especially over long time periods."
msgstr ""
"Caruman bulanan yang konsisten selalunya boleh menyumbang lebih banyak "
"kepada baki akhir anda daripada pelaburan awal anda, terutamanya dalam "
"tempoh masa yang panjang."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:227
msgid "What interest rate should I use?"
msgstr "Apakah kadar faedah yang perlu saya gunakan?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:233
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Stock market average: ~7-10%% annually. Bonds: ~3-5%%. Savings accounts: "
"~4-5%%. Use conservative estimates for long-term planning."
msgstr ""
"Purata pasaran saham: ~7-10%% setiap tahun. Bon: ~3-5%%. Akaun simpanan: "
"~4-5%%. Gunakan anggaran konservatif untuk perancangan jangka panjang."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:239
msgid "Does this account for inflation?"
msgstr "Adakah ini menyumbang kepada inflasi?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/future_value_calculator.html:245
#, python-format
msgid ""
"No, this shows nominal future value. For real (inflation-adjusted) value, "
"subtract expected inflation (~2-3%%) from your interest rate."
msgstr ""
"Tidak, ini menunjukkan nilai masa hadapan nominal. Untuk nilai sebenar "
"(dilaraskan inflasi), tolak jangkaan inflasi (~2-3%%) daripada kadar faedah "
"anda."

