"purchasing power of money. A 3%% inflation rate means prices rise 3%% per "
"year on average."
msgstr ""
"Inflasi ialah kadar di mana harga meningkat dari semasa ke semasa, "
"mengurangkan kuasa beli wang. Kadar inflasi 3%% bermakna harga naik 3%% "
"setahun secara purata."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/inflation_calculator.html:214
msgid "How can I protect against inflation?"
msgstr "Bagaimanakah saya boleh melindungi daripada inflasi?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/inflation_calculator.html:220
msgid ""
"Invest in assets that historically outpace inflation: stocks, real estate, "
"I-bonds, TIPS. Keeping all savings in cash loses value over time due to "
"inflation."
msgstr ""
"Melabur dalam aset yang mengikut sejarah mengatasi inflasi: saham, hartanah,"
" I-bon, TIPS. Menyimpan semua simpanan dalam bentuk tunai kehilangan nilai "
"dari semasa ke semasa disebabkan oleh inflasi."

