#: Financial_Calculators/views/index.py:17
msgid "Mortgage Payoff Calculator"
msgstr "Kalkulator Bayaran Gadai Janji"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:5
msgid "Calculate Payoff Date & Savings"
msgstr "Kira Tarikh Bayaran & Simpanan"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Free mortgage payoff calculator to find when your mortgage will be paid off."
" See how extra payments, biweekly payments, or lump sums can save you money."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator bayaran gadai janji percuma untuk mengetahui bila gadai janji "
"anda akan dibayar. Lihat bagaimana pembayaran tambahan, pembayaran dua "
"mingguan atau jumlah sekali gus boleh menjimatkan wang anda."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"mortgage payoff calculator, early mortgage payoff, extra payment calculator,"
" biweekly payment savings, mortgage interest savings"
msgstr ""
"kalkulator bayaran gadai janji, bayaran gadai janji awal, kalkulator bayaran"
" tambahan, simpanan bayaran dua mingguan, simpanan faedah gadai janji"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate when your mortgage will be paid off and see how extra payments "
"save money."
msgstr ""
"Kira bila gadai janji anda akan dibayar dan lihat cara pembayaran tambahan "
"menjimatkan wang."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:23
msgid "Calculate mortgage payoff date and savings with extra payments"
msgstr ""
"Kira tarikh pembayaran gadai janji dan simpanan dengan bayaran tambahan"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:38
msgid "How do extra payments save money?"
msgstr "Bagaimanakah pembayaran tambahan menjimatkan wang?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:41
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly to principal, reducing the balance that accrues "
"interest. This means you pay less interest overall and finish your loan "
"faster."
msgstr ""
"Bayaran tambahan terus kepada prinsipal, mengurangkan baki yang terakru "
"faedah. Ini bermakna anda membayar kurang faedah secara keseluruhan dan "
"menyelesaikan pinjaman anda dengan lebih cepat."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:46
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:507
msgid "What are biweekly payments?"
msgstr "Apakah bayaran dua minggu sekali?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:49
msgid ""
"Biweekly payments mean paying half your monthly payment every two weeks. "
"With 52 weeks per year, you make 26 half-payments (13 full payments) instead"
" of 12."
msgstr ""
"Pembayaran dwimingguan bermakna membayar separuh bayaran bulanan anda setiap"
" dua minggu. Dengan 52 minggu setahun, anda membuat 26 separuh pembayaran "
"(13 pembayaran penuh) dan bukannya 12."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:76
msgid ""
"Calculate how extra payments or biweekly payments can save on interest and "
"shorten your mortgage term."
msgstr ""
"Kira bagaimana pembayaran tambahan atau pembayaran dua minggu boleh "
"menjimatkan faedah dan memendekkan tempoh gadai janji anda."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:87
msgid "Know Remaining Term"
msgstr "Tahu Baki Penggal"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:90
msgid "Don't Know Term"
msgstr "Istilah Tidak Tahu"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_payoff_calculator.html:97
msgid "Use this for new loans or loans without extra payments made."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan ini untuk pinjaman baru atau pinjaman tanpa bayaran tambahan dibuat."

