#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:379
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:355
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/overweight_calculator.html:368
msgid "BMI Value"
msgstr "Nilai BMI"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:381
msgid ""
"Your calculated BMI number. Lower values indicate lower body weight relative"
" to height."
msgstr ""
"Nombor BMI anda yang dikira. Nilai yang lebih rendah menunjukkan berat badan"
" yang lebih rendah berbanding ketinggian."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:385
msgid "Category & Severity"
msgstr "Kategori & Keterukan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:387
msgid ""
"Shows which BMI range you fall into and the severity level. This helps "
"identify if professional consultation is recommended."
msgstr ""
"Menunjukkan julat BMI yang anda gunakan dan tahap keterukan. Ini membantu "
"mengenal pasti jika perundingan profesional disyorkan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:391
msgid "Healthy Weight Minimum"
msgstr "Berat Sihat Minimum"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:393
msgid ""
"The minimum weight (at BMI 18.5) considered healthy for your height. This is"
" a target for gradual, supervised weight restoration if needed."
msgstr ""
"Berat minimum (pada BMI 18.5) dianggap sihat untuk ketinggian anda. Ini "
"adalah sasaran untuk pemulihan berat badan secara beransur-ansur dan diawasi"
" jika perlu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:399
msgid ""
"The difference between your current weight and the minimum healthy weight. "
"This is informational only—weight restoration should always be supervised by"
" healthcare professionals."
msgstr ""
"Perbezaan antara berat semasa anda dan berat minimum sihat. Ini adalah "
"maklumat sahaja—pemulihan berat badan hendaklah sentiasa diawasi oleh "
"profesional penjagaan kesihatan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:407
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/army_body_fat_calculator.html:369
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:383
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/age_calculator.html:422
msgid "Understanding the Charts"
msgstr "Memahami Carta"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:410
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:386
msgid "BMI Gauge Chart"
msgstr "Carta Tolok BMI"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:412
msgid ""
"A circular gauge showing your BMI value visually. The color corresponds to "
"your category (red for severe, orange for anorexia, yellow for underweight, "
"green for normal)."
msgstr ""
"Tolok bulat yang menunjukkan nilai BMI anda secara visual. Warna sepadan "
"dengan kategori anda (merah untuk teruk, oren untuk anoreksia, kuning untuk "
"kurang berat badan, hijau untuk normal)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:416
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:392
msgid "BMI Categories Chart"
msgstr "Carta Kategori BMI"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:418
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:394
msgid ""
"A horizontal bar chart showing all BMI categories. Your current category is "
"highlighted, making it easy to see where you fall on the spectrum."
msgstr ""
"Carta bar mendatar menunjukkan semua kategori BMI. Kategori semasa anda "
"diserlahkan, menjadikannya mudah untuk melihat tempat anda berada pada "
"spektrum."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:422
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:398
msgid "Healthy Weight Range Chart"
msgstr "Carta Julat Berat Badan Sihat"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:424
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Shows your current weight compared to the healthy weight range for your "
"height. Green bars indicate the healthy range, while your current weight is "
"shown in a color matching your BMI category."
msgstr ""
"Menunjukkan berat semasa anda berbanding dengan julat berat yang sihat untuk"
" ketinggian anda. Bar hijau menunjukkan julat yang sihat, manakala berat "
"semasa anda ditunjukkan dalam warna yang sepadan dengan kategori BMI anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:430
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:406
msgid ""
"A visual scale showing all BMI ranges with a marker indicating your current "
"position. This provides a quick, at-a-glance understanding of your BMI "
"status."
msgstr ""
"Skala visual yang menunjukkan semua julat BMI dengan penanda yang "
"menunjukkan kedudukan semasa anda. Ini memberikan pemahaman yang cepat dan "
"sepintas lalu tentang status BMI anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:444
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:464
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. It is "
"not a diagnostic tool."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator ini adalah untuk tujuan pendidikan dan maklumat sahaja. Ia bukan "
"alat diagnostik."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:450
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmi_calculator.html:470
msgid ""
"BMI does not account for muscle mass, bone density, or body composition. "
"Athletes or individuals with high muscle mass may have higher BMIs that "
"don't reflect excess fat."
msgstr ""
"BMI tidak mengambil kira jisim otot, ketumpatan tulang, atau komposisi "
"badan. Atlet atau individu yang mempunyai jisim otot yang tinggi mungkin "
"mempunyai BMI yang lebih tinggi yang tidak mencerminkan lemak berlebihan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:456
msgid ""
"If you're concerned about an eating disorder or your weight, please seek "
"help from qualified healthcare professionals, registered dietitians, or "
"mental health providers."
msgstr ""
"Jika anda bimbang tentang gangguan pemakanan atau berat badan anda, sila "
"dapatkan bantuan daripada profesional penjagaan kesihatan yang berkelayakan,"
" pakar diet berdaftar atau penyedia kesihatan mental."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:462
msgid ""
"Weight restoration, if needed, should be done gradually and under medical "
"supervision to ensure proper nutrition and avoid refeeding syndrome."
msgstr ""
"Pemulihan berat badan, jika perlu, perlu dilakukan secara beransur-ansur dan"
" di bawah pengawasan perubatan untuk memastikan pemakanan yang betul dan "
"mengelakkan sindrom refeeding."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:469
msgid "When to Seek Professional Help"
msgstr "Bila Perlu Dapatkan Bantuan Profesional"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:471
msgid "Consider consulting a healthcare professional if:"
msgstr ""
"Pertimbangkan untuk berunding dengan profesional penjagaan kesihatan jika:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:474
msgid "Your BMI is below 17.5 (anorexic range)"
msgstr "BMI anda di bawah 17.5 (julat anoreksia)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:475
msgid "You're experiencing rapid weight loss"
msgstr "Anda mengalami penurunan berat badan yang cepat"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:476
msgid "You have concerns about your eating patterns"
msgstr "Anda mempunyai kebimbangan tentang corak pemakanan anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:477
msgid ""
"You're experiencing physical symptoms like fatigue, dizziness, or irregular "
"periods"
msgstr ""
"Anda mengalami gejala fizikal seperti keletihan, pening, atau haid tidak "
"teratur"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:478
msgid ""
"You have persistent thoughts about food, weight, or body image that "
"interfere with daily life"
msgstr ""
"Anda mempunyai pemikiran yang berterusan tentang makanan, berat badan atau "
"imej badan yang mengganggu kehidupan seharian"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:484
msgid "Additional Resources"
msgstr "Sumber Tambahan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:486
msgid ""
"If you or someone you know is struggling with an eating disorder, consider "
"reaching out to:"
msgstr ""
"Jika anda atau seseorang yang anda kenali sedang bergelut dengan gangguan "
"pemakanan, pertimbangkan untuk menghubungi:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:489
msgid "Your primary care physician or family doctor"
msgstr "Doktor penjagaan utama atau doktor keluarga anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:490
msgid "A registered dietitian specializing in eating disorders"
msgstr "Seorang pakar diet berdaftar yang pakar dalam gangguan pemakanan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:491
msgid ""
"A mental health professional (psychologist, psychiatrist, or therapist)"
msgstr ""
"Seorang profesional kesihatan mental (ahli psikologi, pakar psikiatri atau "
"ahli terapi)"

