"Ages 17-20: Max 20%% | Ages 21-27: Max 22%% | Ages 28-39: Max 24%% | Ages "
"40+: Max 26%%"
msgstr ""
"Umur 17-20: Maks 20%% | Umur 21-27: Maks 22%% | Umur 28-39: Maks 24%% | Umur"
" 40+: Maks 26%%"

