#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:330
msgid "What is Blood Alcohol Content (BAC)?"
msgstr "Apakah Kandungan Alkohol Darah (BAC)?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:332
msgid ""
"Blood Alcohol Content (BAC) is a measure of the amount of alcohol in your "
"bloodstream, expressed as a percentage. It's used to determine legal "
"intoxication levels and assess impairment."
msgstr ""
"Kandungan Alkohol Darah (BAC) ialah ukuran jumlah alkohol dalam aliran darah"
" anda, dinyatakan sebagai peratusan. Ia digunakan untuk menentukan tahap "
"mabuk undang-undang dan menilai kemerosotan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:335
#, python-format
msgid ""
"BAC is measured in grams of alcohol per 100 milliliters of blood. For "
"example, a BAC of 0.08%% means 0.08 grams of alcohol per 100 milliliters of "
"blood."
msgstr ""
"BAC diukur dalam gram alkohol setiap 100 mililiter darah. Sebagai contoh, "
"BAC sebanyak 0.08%% bermakna 0.08 gram alkohol setiap 100 mililiter darah."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:341
msgid "Legal BAC Limits"
msgstr "Had BAC Undang-undang"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:344
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:867
msgid "United States"
msgstr "Amerika Syarikat"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:346
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Legal limit: 0.08%% BAC for drivers 21 and over. Zero tolerance "
"(0.00-0.02%%) for drivers under 21."
msgstr ""
"Had undang-undang: 0.08%% BAC untuk pemandu 21 tahun ke atas. Toleransi "
"sifar (0.00-0.02%%) untuk pemandu di bawah 21 tahun."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:350
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:873
msgid "Canada"
msgstr "Kanada"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:352
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Legal limit: 0.08%% BAC (0.05%% in some provinces). Zero tolerance for "
"drivers under 21 or with learner's permits."
msgstr ""
"Had undang-undang: 0.08%% BAC (0.05%% di beberapa wilayah). Toleransi sifar "
"untuk pemandu bawah 21 tahun atau dengan permit pelajar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:356
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:868
msgid "United Kingdom"
msgstr "United Kingdom"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:358
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Legal limit: 0.08%% BAC in England, Wales, and Northern Ireland. 0.05%% in "
"Scotland."
msgstr ""
"Had undang-undang: 0.08%% BAC di England, Wales dan Ireland Utara. 0.05%% di"
" Scotland."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:366
msgid "BAC Effects by Level"
msgstr "Kesan BAC mengikut Tahap"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:369
#, python-format
msgid "0.00%% - 0.02%%: No Effects"
msgstr "0.00%% - 0.02%%: Tiada Kesan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:371
msgid "No noticeable effects. Safe to drive (if legally allowed)."
msgstr ""
"Tiada kesan ketara. Selamat untuk memandu (jika dibenarkan di sisi undang-"
"undang)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:375
#, python-format
msgid "0.02%% - 0.05%%: Mild Effects"
msgstr "0.02%% - 0.05%%: Kesan Ringan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:377
msgid ""
"Slight relaxation, mild mood elevation. Judgment and coordination may be "
"slightly impaired."
msgstr ""
"Kelonggaran sedikit, peningkatan mood yang sederhana. Penghakiman dan "
"penyelarasan mungkin sedikit terjejas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:381
#, python-format
msgid "0.05%% - 0.08%%: Impaired"
msgstr "0.05%% - 0.08%%: Merosot"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:383
msgid ""
"Reduced coordination, impaired judgment, decreased alertness. NOT safe to "
"drive."
msgstr ""
"Penyelarasan berkurangan, penghakiman terjejas, kewaspadaan berkurangan. "
"TIDAK selamat untuk dipandu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:387
#, python-format
msgid "0.08%% - 0.15%%: Significantly Impaired"
msgstr "0.08%% - 0.15%%: Merosot Ketara"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:389
msgid ""
"Poor muscle coordination, balance problems, significantly impaired judgment."
" Illegal to drive."
msgstr ""
"Koordinasi otot yang lemah, masalah keseimbangan, penghakiman terjejas "
"dengan ketara. Haram memandu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:393
#, python-format
msgid "0.15%%+: Severely Impaired"
msgstr "0.15%%+: Teruk terjejas"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:395
msgid ""
"Severe motor impairment, loss of physical control, possible blackouts. "
"Medical attention may be needed."
msgstr ""
"Kerosakan motor yang teruk, kehilangan kawalan fizikal, kemungkinan pitam. "
"Perhatian perubatan mungkin diperlukan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:405
msgid "Select your gender (affects alcohol metabolism)"
msgstr "Pilih jantina anda (menjejaskan metabolisme alkohol)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:406
msgid "Choose weight unit (kg or lbs) and enter your weight"
msgstr "Pilih unit berat (kg atau lbs) dan masukkan berat anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:407
msgid "Enter the number of standard drinks consumed"
msgstr "Masukkan bilangan minuman standard yang digunakan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:408
msgid "Select the type of drink (beer, wine, or liquor)"
msgstr "Pilih jenis minuman (bir, wain atau minuman keras)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:409
msgid "Enter hours since your first drink"
msgstr "Masukkan jam sejak minuman pertama anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:410
msgid "Click 'Calculate BAC' to see your results"
msgstr "Klik 'Kira BAC' untuk melihat keputusan anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:411
msgid "Review charts and wait time before driving"
msgstr "Semak carta dan masa menunggu sebelum memandu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:417
msgid "What is a Standard Drink?"
msgstr "Apakah Minuman Standard?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"A standard drink contains approximately 14 grams (0.6 ounces) of pure "
"alcohol. Examples:"
msgstr ""
"Minuman standard mengandungi kira-kira 14 gram (0.6 auns) alkohol tulen. "
"Contoh:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:424
#, python-format
msgid "Beer: 12 ounces (355 ml) of regular beer (5%% ABV)"
msgstr "Bir: 12 auns (355 ml) bir biasa (5%% ABV)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:428
#, python-format
msgid "Wine: 5 ounces (148 ml) of wine (12%% ABV)"
msgstr "Wain: 5 auns (148 ml) wain (12%% ABV)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:432
#, python-format
msgid "Liquor: 1.5 ounces (44 ml) of distilled spirits (40%% ABV)"
msgstr "Minuman keras: 1.5 auns (44 ml) roh suling (40%% ABV)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:436
msgid ""
"Note: Actual alcohol content varies by brand and type. This calculator uses "
"average values."
msgstr ""
"Nota: Kandungan alkohol sebenar berbeza mengikut jenama dan jenis. "
"Kalkulator ini menggunakan nilai purata."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:442
msgid "Widmark Formula"
msgstr "Formula Widmark"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:444
msgid "This calculator uses the Widmark formula to estimate BAC:"
msgstr "Kalkulator ini menggunakan formula Widmark untuk menganggarkan BAC:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:447
msgid "BAC = (Alcohol in grams / (Weight in kg × r)) - (β × Hours)"
msgstr "BAC = (Alkohol dalam gram / (Berat dalam kg × r)) - (β × Jam)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:450
msgid "Distribution ratio (0.68 for men, 0.55 for women)"
msgstr "Nisbah pengedaran (0.68 untuk lelaki, 0.55 untuk wanita)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:451
msgid "Elimination rate (0.15 g/L per hour average)"
msgstr "Kadar penyingkiran (purata 0.15 g/L sejam)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:454
msgid ""
"The formula accounts for alcohol absorption, distribution in the body, and "
"elimination over time."
msgstr ""
"Formula menyumbang kepada penyerapan alkohol, pengedaran dalam badan, dan "
"penyingkiran dari semasa ke semasa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:463
msgid "BAC Percentage"
msgstr "Peratusan BAC"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:465
msgid ""
"Your estimated blood alcohol content. This is an estimate and may vary based"
" on individual factors."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran kandungan alkohol dalam darah anda. Ini adalah anggaran dan mungkin"
" berbeza-beza berdasarkan faktor individu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:471
msgid ""
"Estimated hours until your BAC reaches zero. Only time can lower BAC - "
"coffee, food, or exercise do not speed up elimination."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran jam sehingga BAC anda mencapai sifar. Hanya masa boleh menurunkan "
"BAC - kopi, makanan atau senaman tidak mempercepatkan penyingkiran."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:475
msgid "Legal Limit Status"
msgstr "Status Had Undang-undang"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:477
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Indicates whether your BAC is above or below the legal driving limit (0.08%%"
" in most US states)."
msgstr ""
"Menunjukkan sama ada BAC anda melebihi atau di bawah had memandu yang sah "
"(0.08%% di kebanyakan negeri AS)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:485
msgid "⚠️ Important Safety Warnings"
msgstr "⚠️ Amaran Keselamatan Penting"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:491
msgid ""
"This calculator provides ESTIMATES only. Actual BAC can vary significantly "
"based on metabolism, food intake, medication, and other factors."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator ini menyediakan ANGGARAN sahaja. BAC sebenar boleh berbeza dengan"
" ketara berdasarkan metabolisme, pengambilan makanan, ubat-ubatan dan faktor"
" lain."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:497
msgid ""
"NEVER drink and drive. If you've consumed any alcohol, arrange for a "
"designated driver, use public transportation, or call a taxi/ride-share "
"service."
msgstr ""
"JANGAN sesekali minum dan memandu. Jika anda telah mengambil apa-apa "
"alkohol, aturkan pemandu yang ditetapkan, gunakan pengangkutan awam atau "
"hubungi perkhidmatan teksi/kongsi perjalanan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:503
msgid ""
"Only time can lower BAC. Coffee, cold showers, food, or exercise do NOT "
"reduce BAC or make you sober."
msgstr ""
"Hanya masa boleh menurunkan BAC. Kopi, mandi air sejuk, makanan atau senaman"
" TIDAK mengurangkan BAC atau membuatkan anda sedar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:509
msgid ""
"Drinking and driving is illegal and dangerous. Penalties include fines, "
"license suspension, and imprisonment. You could kill yourself or others."
msgstr ""
"Minum dan memandu adalah haram dan berbahaya. Penalti termasuk denda, "
"penggantungan lesen, dan penjara. Anda boleh membunuh diri sendiri atau "
"orang lain."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:516
msgid "Factors That Affect BAC"
msgstr "Faktor-faktor yang Mempengaruhi BAC"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:518
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/lean_body_mass_calculator.html:89
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:89
msgid "Body Weight"
msgstr "Berat Badan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:518
msgid ""
"Heavier people generally have lower BAC for the same amount of alcohol."
msgstr ""
"Orang yang lebih berat biasanya mempunyai BAC yang lebih rendah untuk jumlah"
" alkohol yang sama."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:519
msgid ""
"Women typically have higher BAC than men for the same amount of alcohol due "
"to body composition differences."
msgstr ""
"Wanita biasanya mempunyai BAC yang lebih tinggi daripada lelaki untuk jumlah"
" alkohol yang sama disebabkan oleh perbezaan komposisi badan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:520
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:294
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:326
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:330
msgid "Food"
msgstr "Makanan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:520
msgid "Eating before or while drinking slows alcohol absorption."
msgstr "Makan sebelum atau semasa minum melambatkan penyerapan alkohol."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:521
msgid "Metabolism"
msgstr "Metabolisme"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:521
msgid ""
"Individual metabolic rates vary, affecting how quickly alcohol is processed."
msgstr ""
"Kadar metabolisme individu berbeza-beza, mempengaruhi seberapa cepat alkohol"
" diproses."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:522
msgid "Medications"
msgstr "Ubat-ubatan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:522
msgid "Some medications can interact with alcohol and increase impairment."
msgstr ""
"Sesetengah ubat boleh berinteraksi dengan alkohol dan meningkatkan "
"kemerosotan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:523
msgid "Rate of Consumption"
msgstr "Kadar Penggunaan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:523
msgid "Drinking quickly increases BAC faster than drinking slowly."
msgstr ""
"Minum dengan cepat meningkatkan BAC lebih cepat daripada minum perlahan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:640
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:918
msgid "hrs"
msgstr "jam"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:642
msgid "Zero"
msgstr "Sifar"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:650
msgid "Under Limit"
msgstr "Di Bawah Had"

