msgstr "Beri perhatian kepada saiz bahagian"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:472
msgid ""
"Body types are generalizations. Most people are a combination of types "
"rather than purely one type."
msgstr ""
"Jenis badan adalah generalisasi. Kebanyakan orang adalah gabungan jenis dan "
"bukannya satu jenis semata-mata."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:478
msgid ""
"Your body type doesn't determine your fitness potential. With proper "
"nutrition and exercise, anyone can achieve their fitness goals regardless of"
" body type."
msgstr ""
"Jenis badan anda tidak menentukan potensi kecergasan anda. Dengan pemakanan "
"dan senaman yang betul, sesiapa sahaja boleh mencapai matlamat kecergasan "
"mereka tanpa mengira jenis badan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:484
msgid ""
"Body type classifications are based on frame size measurements and are "
"estimates. Individual variations exist."
msgstr ""
"Pengelasan jenis badan adalah berdasarkan ukuran saiz bingkai dan merupakan "
"anggaran. Variasi individu wujud."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:490
