msgstr ""
"Kalkulator mencadangkan untuk mengagihkan kalori harian anda pada makanan "
"seperti berikut:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:490
#, python-format
msgid "Breakfast (25%%):"
msgstr "Sarapan pagi (25%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:490
msgid "Start your day with a balanced meal to fuel your morning activities."
msgstr ""
"Mulakan hari anda dengan makanan yang seimbang untuk menyemarakkan aktiviti "
"pagi anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:491
#, python-format
msgid "Lunch (35%%):"
msgstr "Makan tengah hari (35%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:491
msgid "Your largest meal, providing energy for the afternoon."
msgstr "Hidangan terbesar anda, membekalkan tenaga untuk petang."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:492
#, python-format
msgid "Dinner (30%%):"
msgstr "Makan malam (30%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:492
msgid "Evening meal to support recovery and prevent late-night hunger."
msgstr ""
"Makan malam untuk menyokong pemulihan dan mengelakkan kelaparan lewat malam."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:493
#, python-format
msgid "Snacks (10%%):"
msgstr "Makanan ringan (10%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:493
msgid "Small snacks throughout the day to maintain energy levels."
msgstr "Makanan ringan kecil sepanjang hari untuk mengekalkan tahap tenaga."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:496
msgid ""
"Note: Meal distribution is flexible. Adjust based on your schedule and "
"preferences while maintaining your total daily calorie target."
msgstr ""
"Nota: Pengagihan makanan adalah fleksibel. Laraskan berdasarkan jadual dan "
"pilihan anda sambil mengekalkan jumlah sasaran kalori harian anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:507
msgid ""
"The total number of calories you should consume daily to achieve your "
"selected goal. This is your TDEE adjusted by the goal-specific calorie "
"change."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah kalori yang perlu anda ambil setiap hari untuk mencapai matlamat yang"
" anda pilih. Ini ialah TDEE anda yang diselaraskan oleh perubahan kalori "
"khusus matlamat."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:511
msgid "Weekly Projection"
msgstr "Unjuran Mingguan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:513
msgid ""
"An estimate of how much weight you'll lose or gain per week based on your "
"calorie deficit or surplus. A deficit of 500 calories per day typically "
"results in ~0.5 kg (1 lb) weight loss per week."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran berapa banyak berat badan anda akan turun atau naik setiap minggu "
"berdasarkan defisit atau lebihan kalori anda. Defisit 500 kalori sehari "
"biasanya mengakibatkan ~0.5 kg (1 lb) penurunan berat badan setiap minggu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:517
msgid "Macronutrient Breakdown"
msgstr "Pecahan Makronutrien"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:519
msgid ""
"The recommended distribution of protein, carbohydrates, and fat based on "
"your goal. Macros are adjusted to optimize results for weight loss, "
"maintenance, or weight gain."
msgstr ""
"Pengagihan protein, karbohidrat dan lemak yang disyorkan berdasarkan "
"matlamat anda. Makro dilaraskan untuk mengoptimumkan hasil untuk penurunan "
"berat badan, penyelenggaraan atau penambahan berat badan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:525
msgid ""
"Suggested calorie distribution across meals throughout the day. This helps "
"you plan your meals and maintain consistent energy levels."
msgstr ""
"Cadangan pengagihan kalori merentasi hidangan sepanjang hari. Ini membantu "
"anda merancang makanan anda dan mengekalkan tahap tenaga yang konsisten."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:533
msgid "Tips for Success"
msgstr "Petua untuk Berjaya"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:535
msgid "Track Your Food:"
msgstr "Jejaki Makanan Anda:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:535
msgid ""
"Use a food tracking app to monitor your calorie intake and ensure you're "
"meeting your targets."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan apl penjejakan makanan untuk memantau pengambilan kalori anda dan "
"memastikan anda mencapai sasaran anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:536
msgid "Be Consistent:"
msgstr "Jadilah Konsisten:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:536
msgid ""
"Consistency is key. Aim to hit your calorie target most days of the week."
msgstr ""
"Konsisten adalah kunci. Bertujuan untuk mencapai sasaran kalori anda pada "
"kebanyakan hari dalam seminggu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:537
msgid "Adjust as Needed:"
msgstr "Laraskan mengikut keperluan:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:537
msgid ""
"Monitor your progress and adjust calories if you're not seeing desired "
"results after 2-3 weeks."
msgstr ""
"Pantau kemajuan anda dan laraskan kalori jika anda tidak melihat hasil yang "
"diingini selepas 2-3 minggu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:538
msgid "Focus on Whole Foods:"
msgstr "Fokus pada Makanan Keseluruhan:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:538
msgid ""
"Prioritize nutrient-dense whole foods over processed foods for better health"
" and satiety."
msgstr ""
"Utamakan makanan keseluruhan padat nutrien daripada makanan yang diproses "
"untuk kesihatan dan kenyang yang lebih baik."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:539
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:376
msgid "Stay Hydrated:"
msgstr "Kekal Terhidrat:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:539
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:376
msgid ""
"Drink plenty of water throughout the day. Sometimes thirst is mistaken for "
"hunger."
msgstr ""
"Minum banyak air sepanjang hari. Kadang-kadang dahaga disalah anggap sebagai"
" lapar."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:540
msgid "Combine with Exercise:"
msgstr "Gabungkan dengan Senaman:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:540
msgid "Regular exercise enhances your results and improves overall health."
msgstr ""
"Senaman yang kerap meningkatkan keputusan anda dan meningkatkan kesihatan "
"keseluruhan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:552
msgid ""
"Calorie calculations are estimates. Individual metabolism can vary based on "
"genetics, muscle mass, hormones, and other factors."
msgstr ""
"Pengiraan kalori adalah anggaran. Metabolisme individu boleh berbeza-beza "
"berdasarkan genetik, jisim otot, hormon, dan faktor lain."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:564
msgid ""
"Extreme calorie deficits or surpluses may not be sustainable or healthy. "
"Consult with a healthcare provider or registered dietitian for personalized "
"advice."
msgstr ""
"Defisit atau lebihan kalori yang melampau mungkin tidak mampan atau sihat. "
"Rujuk dengan pembekal penjagaan kesihatan atau pakar diet berdaftar untuk "
"mendapatkan nasihat peribadi."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:570
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:468
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:505
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/healthy_weight_calculator.html:408
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. It "
"should not replace professional medical or nutritional advice."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator ini adalah untuk tujuan pendidikan dan maklumat sahaja. Ia tidak "
"seharusnya menggantikan nasihat perubatan atau pemakanan profesional."

