#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:320
msgid "What are Carbohydrates?"
msgstr "Apakah Karbohidrat?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:322
msgid ""
"Carbohydrates are one of the three main macronutrients (along with protein "
"and fat) that provide energy to your body. They are broken down into "
"glucose, which is the primary fuel source for your brain and muscles."
msgstr ""
"Karbohidrat adalah salah satu daripada tiga makronutrien utama (bersama "
"protein dan lemak) yang membekalkan tenaga kepada badan anda. Mereka "
"dipecahkan kepada glukosa, yang merupakan sumber bahan api utama untuk otak "
"dan otot anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:325
msgid ""
"Carbohydrates provide 4 calories per gram and are found in foods like "
"grains, fruits, vegetables, legumes, and dairy products. They play a crucial"
" role in maintaining energy levels, supporting physical performance, and "
"fueling brain function."
msgstr ""
"Karbohidrat membekalkan 4 kalori setiap gram dan terdapat dalam makanan "
"seperti bijirin, buah-buahan, sayur-sayuran, kekacang dan produk tenusu. "
"Mereka memainkan peranan penting dalam mengekalkan tahap tenaga, menyokong "
"prestasi fizikal, dan menyemarakkan fungsi otak."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:331
msgid "Types of Carbohydrates"
msgstr "Jenis Karbohidrat"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:334
msgid "Simple Carbohydrates"
msgstr "Karbohidrat Mudah"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:336
msgid ""
"Quick-digesting carbs found in fruits, milk, and processed foods. Provide "
"rapid energy but can cause blood sugar spikes."
msgstr ""
"Karbohidrat penghadaman cepat yang terdapat dalam buah-buahan, susu dan "
"makanan yang diproses. Membekalkan tenaga yang cepat tetapi boleh "
"menyebabkan lonjakan gula dalam darah."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:338
msgid "Examples: Sugar, honey, fruit juice, white bread"
msgstr "Contoh: Gula, madu, jus buah, roti putih"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:341
msgid "Complex Carbohydrates"
msgstr "Karbohidrat Kompleks"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Slow-digesting carbs found in whole grains, vegetables, and legumes. Provide"
" sustained energy and are rich in fiber."
msgstr ""
"Karbohidrat penghadaman perlahan yang terdapat dalam bijirin penuh, sayur-"
"sayuran dan kekacang. Membekalkan tenaga yang berterusan dan kaya dengan "
"serat."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:345
msgid "Examples: Oats, brown rice, quinoa, sweet potatoes, beans"
msgstr "Contoh: Oat, beras perang, quinoa, keledek, kekacang"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:348
msgid "Fiber"
msgstr "Serat"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:350
msgid ""
"A type of carbohydrate that cannot be digested. Important for digestive "
"health, blood sugar control, and satiety."
msgstr ""
"Sejenis karbohidrat yang tidak boleh dihadam. Penting untuk kesihatan "
"penghadaman, kawalan gula dalam darah dan rasa kenyang."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:352
msgid "Examples: Whole grains, vegetables, fruits, legumes"
msgstr "Contoh: Bijirin penuh, sayur-sayuran, buah-buahan, kekacang"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:361
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:393
msgid "Enter your total daily calorie intake"
msgstr "Masukkan jumlah pengambilan kalori harian anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:362
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/fat_intake_calculator.html:394
msgid "Choose calculation method: By Percentage or From Remaining Macros"
msgstr "Pilih kaedah pengiraan: Mengikut Peratusan atau Daripada Baki Makro"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:363
msgid ""
"If using percentage method, enter your desired carbohydrate percentage (or "
"use the slider)"
msgstr ""
"Jika menggunakan kaedah peratusan, masukkan peratusan karbohidrat yang anda "
"inginkan (atau gunakan peluncur)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:364
msgid ""
"If using remaining macros method, enter your protein and fat percentages"
msgstr ""
"Jika menggunakan kaedah makro yang tinggal, masukkan peratusan protein dan "
"lemak anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:365
msgid "Click 'Calculate Carbs' to see your results"
msgstr "Klik 'Kira Karbohidrat' untuk melihat keputusan anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:366
msgid ""
"Review your daily carbohydrate needs, meal distribution, and food sources"
msgstr ""
"Semak keperluan karbohidrat harian anda, pengedaran makanan dan sumber "
"makanan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:367
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your carbohydrate distribution"
msgstr "Gunakan carta untuk menggambarkan taburan karbohidrat anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:378
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The total amount of carbohydrates (in grams) you should consume daily based "
"on your calorie intake and selected percentage. This is calculated as: "
"(Total Calories × Carb %%) ÷ 4 calories per gram."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah karbohidrat (dalam gram) yang perlu anda makan setiap hari "
"berdasarkan pengambilan kalori dan peratusan yang dipilih. Ini dikira "
"sebagai: (Jumlah Kalori × Karbohidrat %%) ÷ 4 kalori setiap gram."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:382
msgid "Calories from Carbs"
msgstr "Kalori daripada Karbohidrat"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:384
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The number of calories that come from carbohydrates. This is calculated as: "
"Total Calories × (Carb %% ÷ 100)."
msgstr ""
"Bilangan kalori yang datang dari karbohidrat. Ini dikira sebagai: Jumlah "
"Kalori × (Karb %% ÷ 100)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:390
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Suggested carbohydrate distribution across meals: Breakfast (25%%), Lunch "
"(35%%), Dinner (30%%), and Snacks (10%%). This helps maintain steady energy "
"levels throughout the day."
msgstr ""
"Pengagihan karbohidrat yang dicadangkan merentas hidangan: Sarapan (25%%), "
"Makan Tengahari (35%%), Makan Malam (30%%) dan Makanan Ringan (10%%). Ini "
"membantu mengekalkan tahap tenaga yang stabil sepanjang hari."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:396
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Comparison of low carb (10%%), moderate (40%%), and high carb (60%%) "
"approaches. Choose based on your goals, activity level, and personal "
"preferences."
msgstr ""
"Perbandingan pendekatan karbohidrat rendah (10%%), sederhana (40%%) dan "
"karbohidrat tinggi (60%). Pilih berdasarkan matlamat, tahap aktiviti dan "
"pilihan peribadi anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:400
msgid "Carbohydrate Sources"
msgstr "Sumber Karbohidrat"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:402
msgid ""
"A guide showing common carbohydrate sources and how many servings you would "
"need to meet your daily carbohydrate target."
msgstr ""
"Panduan yang menunjukkan sumber karbohidrat biasa dan bilangan hidangan yang"
" anda perlukan untuk memenuhi sasaran karbohidrat harian anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:410
msgid "Carbohydrate Intake Guidelines"
msgstr "Garis Panduan Pengambilan Karbohidrat"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:412
#, python-format
msgid "Low Carb (10-20%%):"
msgstr "Karbohidrat Rendah (10-20%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:412
msgid ""
"Typically 50-150g per day. Suitable for weight loss, ketogenic diets, or "
"managing blood sugar. May require adaptation period."
msgstr ""
"Biasanya 50-150g sehari. Sesuai untuk penurunan berat badan, diet ketogenik,"
" atau menguruskan gula darah. Mungkin memerlukan tempoh penyesuaian."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:413
#, python-format
msgid "Moderate Carb (40-50%%):"
msgstr "Karbohidrat Sederhana (40-50%%):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"Typically 200-300g per day. Balanced approach suitable for most people. "
"Recommended for general health and moderate activity levels."
msgstr ""
"Biasanya 200-300g sehari. Pendekatan seimbang sesuai untuk kebanyakan orang."
" Disyorkan untuk kesihatan umum dan tahap aktiviti sederhana."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:414
#, python-format
msgid "High Carb (60%%+):"
msgstr "Karbohidrat Tinggi (60%%+):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:414
msgid ""
"Typically 300g+ per day. Suitable for athletes, very active individuals, or "
"those with high calorie needs. Supports intense training and recovery."
msgstr ""
"Biasanya 300g+ sehari. Sesuai untuk atlet, individu yang sangat aktif, atau "
"mereka yang memerlukan kalori tinggi. Menyokong latihan dan pemulihan yang "
"sengit."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:420
msgid "Best Carbohydrate Sources"
msgstr "Sumber Karbohidrat Terbaik"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:422
msgid "Whole Grains:"
msgstr "Bijirin Penuh:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:422
msgid ""
"Oats, brown rice, quinoa, whole wheat bread, barley. Rich in fiber and "
"nutrients."
msgstr ""
"Oat, beras perang, quinoa, roti gandum, barli. Kaya dengan serat dan "
"nutrien."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:423
msgid "Starchy Vegetables:"
msgstr "Sayuran berkanji:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:423
msgid ""
"Sweet potatoes, potatoes, corn, peas. Provide energy and essential vitamins."
msgstr ""
"Ubi keledek, kentang, jagung, kacang. Membekalkan tenaga dan vitamin "
"penting."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:424
msgid "Legumes:"
msgstr "Kekacang:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:424
msgid "Beans, lentils, chickpeas. High in fiber and protein."
msgstr "Kacang, lentil, kacang ayam. Tinggi serat dan protein."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:425
msgid "Fruits:"
msgstr "buah-buahan:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"Berries, bananas, apples, oranges. Natural sugars with vitamins and fiber."
msgstr "Beri, pisang, epal, oren. Gula semulajadi dengan vitamin dan serat."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:426
msgid "Dairy:"
msgstr "tenusu:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:426
msgid ""
"Milk, yogurt. Contains lactose (natural sugar) plus protein and calcium."
msgstr ""
"Susu, yogurt. Mengandungi laktosa (gula semulajadi) ditambah protein dan "
"kalsium."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:432
msgid "Tips for Optimal Carbohydrate Intake"
msgstr "Petua Pengambilan Karbohidrat Optimum"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:434
msgid "Choose Complex Carbs:"
msgstr "Pilih Karbohidrat Kompleks:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Prioritize whole grains, vegetables, and legumes over refined and processed "
"carbohydrates."
msgstr ""
"Utamakan bijirin penuh, sayur-sayuran dan kekacang berbanding karbohidrat "
"yang ditapis dan diproses."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:435
msgid "Time Your Carbs:"
msgstr "Masa Karbohidrat Anda:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:435
msgid ""
"Consume most carbs around workouts for optimal performance and recovery."
msgstr ""
"Ambil kebanyakan karbohidrat semasa bersenam untuk prestasi dan pemulihan "
"yang optimum."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:436
msgid "Include Fiber:"
msgstr "Sertakan Serat:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/carbohydrate_calculator.html:436
msgid ""
"Aim for 25-35g of fiber daily from carbohydrate sources for digestive "
"health."
msgstr ""
"Sasarkan 25-35g serat setiap hari daripada sumber karbohidrat untuk "
"kesihatan pencernaan."

