msgstr "Tolok Kepantasan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:259
msgid "Speed Comparison"
msgstr "Perbandingan Kelajuan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:273
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:396
msgid "Race Time Predictions"
msgstr "Ramalan Masa Perlumbaan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:282
msgid "Common Race Distances"
msgstr "Jarak Perlumbaan Bersama"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:290
msgid "Pace Category"
msgstr "Kategori Pace"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:311
msgid "What is Running Pace?"
msgstr "Apakah Running Pace?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:313
msgid ""
"Running pace is the time it takes to cover a specific distance, typically "
"expressed as minutes per kilometer (min/km) or minutes per mile (min/mi). "
"It's a fundamental metric for runners to track performance, plan training, "
"and predict race times."
msgstr ""
"Larian laju ialah masa yang diperlukan untuk menempuh jarak tertentu, "
"biasanya dinyatakan sebagai minit setiap kilometer (min/km) atau minit "
"setiap batu (min/bt). Ia merupakan metrik asas untuk pelari menjejak "
"prestasi, merancang latihan dan meramal masa perlumbaan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:316
msgid "Pace = Time ÷ Distance"
msgstr "Laju = Masa ÷ Jarak"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:319
msgid ""
"For example, if you run 5 kilometers in 30 minutes, your pace is 6 minutes "
"per kilometer (30 ÷ 5 = 6 min/km)."
msgstr ""
"Contohnya, jika anda berlari 5 kilometer dalam 30 minit, kadar anda ialah 6 "
"minit setiap kilometer (30 ÷ 5 = 6 min/km)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:325
msgid "Pace Categories"
msgstr "Kategori Pace"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:328
msgid "Elite: &lt; 3:30 min/km"
msgstr "Elit: &lt; 3:30 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:330
msgid "World-class performance. Professional and elite competitive runners."
msgstr "Prestasi bertaraf dunia. Pelari kompetitif profesional dan elit."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:334
msgid "Advanced: 3:30-4:00 min/km"
msgstr "Maju: 3:30-4:00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:336
msgid ""
"Excellent performance. Highly trained runners with years of experience."
msgstr ""
"Prestasi cemerlang. Pelari terlatih tinggi dengan pengalaman bertahun-tahun."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:340
msgid "Intermediate: 4:00-5:00 min/km"
msgstr "Pertengahan: 4:00-5:00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:342
msgid "Good fitness level. Regular runners with consistent training."
msgstr ""
"Tahap kecergasan yang baik. Pelari tetap dengan latihan yang konsisten."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:346
msgid "Recreational: 5:00-6:00 min/km"
msgstr "Rekreasi: 5:00-6:00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:348
msgid "Healthy activity level. Casual runners maintaining fitness."
msgstr "Tahap aktiviti yang sihat. Pelari kasual mengekalkan kecergasan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:352
msgid "Beginner: 6:00-7:00 min/km"
msgstr "Pemula: 6:00-7:00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:354
msgid "Building fitness. New runners or those returning to running."
msgstr "Membina kecergasan. Pelari baru atau mereka yang kembali berlari."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:358
msgid "Walking: &gt; 7:00 min/km"
msgstr "Berjalan: &gt; 7:00 min/km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:360
msgid "Walking pace. Great for health, recovery, and active rest."
msgstr "Laju berjalan. Bagus untuk kesihatan, pemulihan dan rehat aktif."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:370
msgid "Select calculation type: 'Pace from Time' or 'Time from Pace'"
msgstr "Pilih jenis pengiraan: 'Pace from Time' atau 'Time from Pace'"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:371
msgid "Choose your distance unit (kilometers or miles)"
msgstr "Pilih unit jarak anda (kilometer atau batu)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:372
msgid "Enter your distance and time (or pace)"
msgstr "Masukkan jarak dan masa (atau rentak) anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:374
msgid "Review your pace, speed, and race time predictions"
msgstr "Semak rentak, kelajuan dan ramalan masa perlumbaan anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:375
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your performance"
msgstr "Gunakan carta untuk menggambarkan prestasi anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:384
msgid "Pace per Kilometer/Mile"
msgstr "Kelajuan setiap Kilometer/Batu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:386
msgid ""
"The time it takes to run one kilometer or one mile. Lower numbers mean "
"faster pace. Displayed as minutes:seconds per unit distance."
msgstr ""
"Masa yang diperlukan untuk berlari satu kilometer atau satu batu. Nombor "
"yang lebih rendah bermakna kadar yang lebih pantas. Dipaparkan sebagai "
"minit: saat setiap unit jarak."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:390
msgid "Speed (km/h or mph)"
msgstr "Kelajuan (km/j atau mph)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:392
msgid ""
"Your average running speed. Calculated as distance divided by time. Useful "
"for comparing with other activities like cycling or driving."
msgstr ""
"Kelajuan larian purata anda. Dikira sebagai jarak dibahagikan dengan masa. "
"Berguna untuk membandingkan dengan aktiviti lain seperti berbasikal atau "
"memandu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:398
msgid ""
"Estimated finish times for common race distances (1km, 5km, 10km, half "
"marathon, marathon) based on your current pace. Useful for goal setting and "
"race planning."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran masa penamat untuk jarak perlumbaan biasa (1km, 5km, 10km, separuh "
"maraton, maraton) berdasarkan rentak semasa anda. Berguna untuk penetapan "
"matlamat dan perancangan perlumbaan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:406
msgid "Training Tips"
msgstr "Petua Latihan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:409
msgid "Consistent Training"
msgstr "Latihan Konsisten"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:411
msgid ""
"Regular running improves pace over time. Aim for 3-4 runs per week with "
"gradual distance increases."
msgstr ""
"Larian tetap meningkatkan rentak dari semasa ke semasa. Matlamat untuk 3-4 "
"larian setiap minggu dengan peningkatan jarak secara beransur-ansur."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:415
msgid "Interval Training"
msgstr "Latihan Selang Waktu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:417
msgid ""
"Incorporate speed work (intervals, tempo runs) to improve pace. Mix fast and"
" slow runs for balanced training."
msgstr ""
"Menggabungkan kerja kelajuan (selang masa, larian tempo) untuk meningkatkan "
"rentak. Campurkan larian pantas dan perlahan untuk latihan yang seimbang."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:421
msgid "Recovery"
msgstr "Pemulihan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:423
msgid ""
"Allow adequate rest between hard runs. Recovery is essential for improvement"
" and injury prevention."
msgstr ""
"Benarkan rehat yang mencukupi antara larian keras. Pemulihan adalah penting "
"untuk penambahbaikan dan pencegahan kecederaan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:437
msgid ""
"Pace varies with terrain, weather, elevation, and fitness level. Use this "
"calculator as a guide, not an absolute measure."
msgstr ""
"Kepantasan berbeza-beza mengikut rupa bumi, cuaca, ketinggian dan tahap "
"kecergasan. Gunakan kalkulator ini sebagai panduan, bukan ukuran mutlak."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:443
msgid ""
"Race time predictions assume you can maintain the same pace for longer "
"distances, which may not always be realistic. Adjust expectations based on "
"your training."
msgstr ""
"Ramalan masa perlumbaan menganggap anda boleh mengekalkan rentak yang sama "
"untuk jarak yang lebih jauh, yang mungkin tidak selalu realistik. Laraskan "
"jangkaan berdasarkan latihan anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:449
msgid ""
"For accurate pace tracking, use GPS watches, running apps, or measured "
"courses. Manual calculations are estimates."
msgstr ""
"Untuk penjejakan rentak yang tepat, gunakan jam tangan GPS, apl berjalan "
"atau kursus yang diukur. Pengiraan manual adalah anggaran."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:455
msgid ""
"Always listen to your body. If you experience pain or excessive fatigue, "
"rest and consult with healthcare professionals."
msgstr ""
"Sentiasa mendengar badan anda. Jika anda mengalami kesakitan atau keletihan "
"yang berlebihan, berehat dan berunding dengan profesional penjagaan "
"kesihatan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:631
msgid "1 km"
msgstr "1 km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:632
msgid "5 km"
msgstr "5 km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:633
msgid "10 km"
msgstr "10 km"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:634
msgid "Half Marathon"
msgstr "Separuh Marathon"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pace_calculator.html:635
msgid "Marathon"
msgstr "Marathon"

