#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_the_week_calculator.html:179
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:149
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/day_of_week_calculator.html:179
msgid "Start Date"
msgstr "Tarikh Mula"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:203
msgid "Ovulation & Fertile Window"
msgstr "Ovulasi & Tingkap Subur"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:238
msgid "Cycle Progress"
msgstr "Kemajuan Kitaran"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:252
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:261
msgid "Upcoming Cycles"
msgstr "Kitaran Akan Datang"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:290
msgid "What is the Menstrual Cycle?"
msgstr "Apakah Kitaran Haid?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:292
msgid ""
"The menstrual cycle is a natural process that occurs in the female "
"reproductive system, typically lasting 21-35 days (average 28 days). It "
"involves hormonal changes that prepare the body for potential pregnancy each"
" month."
msgstr ""
"Kitaran haid adalah proses semula jadi yang berlaku dalam sistem pembiakan "
"wanita, biasanya berlangsung 21-35 hari (purata 28 hari). Ia melibatkan "
"perubahan hormon yang menyediakan badan untuk potensi kehamilan setiap "
"bulan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:295
msgid ""
"The cycle begins on the first day of menstruation (period) and ends the day "
"before the next period starts. Understanding your cycle helps with fertility"
" planning, health monitoring, and predicting period dates."
msgstr ""
"Kitaran bermula pada hari pertama haid (haid) dan berakhir sehari sebelum "
"haid seterusnya bermula. Memahami kitaran anda membantu dengan perancangan "
"kesuburan, pemantauan kesihatan dan meramalkan tarikh haid."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:342
msgid ""
"Enter your average period length (how many days your period typically lasts)"
msgstr ""
"Masukkan purata tempoh haid anda (berapa hari tempoh haid anda biasanya)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Click 'Calculate' to see predictions for your next periods, ovulation dates,"
" and fertile windows"
msgstr ""
"Klik 'Kira' untuk melihat ramalan untuk haid anda yang seterusnya, tarikh "
"ovulasi dan tingkap subur"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:344
msgid "Review the cycle calendar and phase distribution charts"
msgstr "Semak kalendar kitaran dan carta taburan fasa"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:345
msgid "Use the predictions to plan ahead and track your cycle"
msgstr "Gunakan ramalan untuk merancang lebih awal dan menjejaki kitaran anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:356
msgid ""
"Predicted start and end dates for your next menstrual period based on your "
"cycle length and last period date."
msgstr ""
"Tarikh mula dan tamat yang diramalkan untuk haid anda yang seterusnya "
"berdasarkan tempoh kitaran dan tarikh terakhir haid anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:362
msgid ""
"Estimated date when ovulation occurs (typically 14 days before your next "
"period). This is your most fertile day."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran tarikh ovulasi berlaku (biasanya 14 hari sebelum haid anda yang "
"seterusnya). Ini adalah hari paling subur anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"The 6-7 day period when conception is most likely. This includes 5 days "
"before ovulation, the day of ovulation, and 1 day after."
msgstr ""
"Tempoh 6-7 hari apabila pembuahan berkemungkinan besar. Ini termasuk 5 hari "
"sebelum ovulasi, hari ovulasi, dan 1 hari selepasnya."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"Shows which day of your current cycle you are on. Day 1 is the first day of "
"your last period."
msgstr ""
"Menunjukkan hari kitaran semasa anda berada. Hari 1 ialah hari pertama haid "
"terakhir anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:382
msgid "Cycle Tracking Tips"
msgstr "Petua Penjejakan Kitaran"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:385
msgid "Consistent Tracking"
msgstr "Penjejakan Konsisten"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:387
msgid ""
"Track your period start dates for at least 3-6 months to get an accurate "
"average cycle length. Mark dates on a calendar or use a period tracking app."
msgstr ""
"Jejaki tarikh mula haid anda untuk sekurang-kurangnya 3-6 bulan untuk "
"mendapatkan purata panjang kitaran yang tepat. Tandakan tarikh pada kalendar"
" atau gunakan apl penjejakan tempoh."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:391
msgid "Note Symptoms"
msgstr "Nota Gejala"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:393
msgid ""
"Track symptoms like cramps, mood changes, and flow intensity. This helps "
"identify patterns and can be useful for healthcare consultations."
msgstr ""
"Jejaki simptom seperti kekejangan, perubahan mood dan keamatan aliran. Ini "
"membantu mengenal pasti corak dan boleh berguna untuk perundingan penjagaan "
"kesihatan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:397
msgid "Irregular Cycles"
msgstr "Kitaran Tidak Teratur"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:399
msgid ""
"If your cycles are very irregular (varying by more than 7 days), consider "
"consulting with a healthcare provider. Irregular cycles can indicate "
"underlying health conditions."
msgstr ""
"Jika kitaran anda sangat tidak teratur (berbeza-beza melebihi 7 hari), "
"pertimbangkan untuk berunding dengan pembekal penjagaan kesihatan. Kitaran "
"yang tidak teratur boleh menunjukkan keadaan kesihatan yang mendasari."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"Period calculators provide estimates based on average cycle patterns. Actual"
" timing can vary due to stress, illness, travel, hormonal changes, or "
"medical conditions."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator tempoh menyediakan anggaran berdasarkan corak kitaran purata. "
"Masa sebenar boleh berbeza-beza disebabkan oleh tekanan, penyakit, "
"perjalanan, perubahan hormon atau keadaan perubatan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"If you have irregular cycles, PCOS, endometriosis, or other reproductive "
"health concerns, consult with a healthcare provider or gynecologist for "
"personalized guidance."
msgstr ""
"Jika anda mempunyai kitaran yang tidak teratur, PCOS, endometriosis atau "
"masalah kesihatan reproduktif lain, berunding dengan pembekal penjagaan "
"kesihatan atau pakar sakit puan untuk mendapatkan bimbingan yang "
"diperibadikan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:431
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical advice. Always consult healthcare providers for "
"reproductive health concerns, fertility planning, or if you experience "
"unusual symptoms."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator ini adalah untuk tujuan maklumat sahaja dan tidak boleh "
"menggantikan nasihat perubatan profesional. Sentiasa berunding dengan "
"penyedia penjagaan kesihatan untuk masalah kesihatan reproduktif, "
"perancangan kesuburan, atau jika anda mengalami gejala luar biasa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:556
msgid "complete"
msgstr "lengkap"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:608
msgid "Cycle"
msgstr "Kitaran"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:611
msgid "Period"
msgstr "Tempoh"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:615
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:364
msgid "Ovulation"
msgstr "Ovulasi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:48
msgid "Pregnancy Calculator"
msgstr "Kalkulator Kehamilan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:14
msgid "Comprehensive Pregnancy Tracker"
msgstr "Penjejak Kehamilan Komprehensif"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Track your pregnancy with our comprehensive calculator. Calculate due date, "
"weeks pregnant, trimester, milestones, and appointments."
msgstr ""
"Kesan kehamilan anda dengan kalkulator komprehensif kami. Kira tarikh akhir,"
" minggu mengandung, trimester, peristiwa penting dan janji temu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"pregnancy calculator, pregnancy tracker, due date calculator, weeks "
"pregnant, trimester calculator"
msgstr ""
"kalkulator kehamilan, penjejak kehamilan, kalkulator tarikh akhir, minggu "
"hamil, kalkulator trimester"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:15
msgid "Track your pregnancy with comprehensive calculations and milestones."
msgstr ""
"Jejaki kehamilan anda dengan pengiraan dan pencapaian yang komprehensif."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:24
msgid "Comprehensive pregnancy tracking and calculations"
msgstr "Pengesanan dan pengiraan kehamilan yang komprehensif"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Track your pregnancy with comprehensive calculations. Calculate due date, "
"weeks pregnant, trimester, fetal development milestones, and upcoming "
"appointments."
msgstr ""
"Jejaki kehamilan anda dengan pengiraan yang komprehensif. Kira tarikh "
"matang, minggu mengandung, trimester, pencapaian perkembangan janin dan "
"janji temu akan datang."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:65
msgid "Pregnancy Information"
msgstr "Maklumat Kehamilan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:162
msgid ""
"Enter your pregnancy information using any calculation method, then click "
"Calculate to see comprehensive tracking details including due date, weeks "
"pregnant, trimester, milestones, and appointments."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan maklumat kehamilan anda menggunakan sebarang kaedah pengiraan, "
"kemudian klik Kira untuk melihat butiran penjejakan yang komprehensif "
"termasuk tarikh akhir, minggu kehamilan, trimester, peristiwa penting dan "
"janji temu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:246
msgid "Milestones Progress"
msgstr "Pencapaian Kemajuan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:262
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:294
msgid "Trimester Progress"
msgstr "Kemajuan Trimester"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:275
msgid "Weeks Progress"
msgstr "Kemajuan Minggu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:285
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:392
msgid "Fetal Development Milestones"
msgstr "Pencapaian Perkembangan Janin"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:293
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:398
msgid "Upcoming Appointments"
msgstr "Janji Temu Akan Datang"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:322
msgid "What is a Pregnancy Calculator?"
msgstr "Apakah itu Kalkulator Kehamilan?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:324
msgid ""
"A pregnancy calculator helps you track your pregnancy journey by calculating"
" important dates, milestones, and providing information about fetal "
"development. It uses your last menstrual period (LMP), conception date, or "
"due date to estimate how far along you are in your pregnancy."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator kehamilan membantu anda menjejaki perjalanan kehamilan anda "
"dengan mengira tarikh penting, peristiwa penting dan memberikan maklumat "
"tentang perkembangan janin. Ia menggunakan tempoh haid terakhir anda (LMP), "
"tarikh konsep atau tarikh matang untuk menganggarkan sejauh mana anda berada"
" dalam kehamilan anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:327
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is typically calculated as 40 weeks (280 days) from the first day "
"of your last menstrual period, or 38 weeks (266 days) from conception. This "
"calculator provides comprehensive tracking throughout all three trimesters."
msgstr ""
"Kehamilan biasanya dikira sebagai 40 minggu (280 hari) dari hari pertama "
"haid terakhir anda, atau 38 minggu (266 hari) dari pembuahan. Kalkulator ini"
" menyediakan penjejakan komprehensif sepanjang ketiga-tiga trimester."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:336
msgid "First Trimester (Weeks 1-12)"
msgstr "Trimester Pertama (Minggu 1-12)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:338
msgid ""
"Early development phase. Baby's major organs and body systems are forming. "
"Important time for prenatal care, folic acid, and avoiding harmful "
"substances. Morning sickness and fatigue are common."
msgstr ""
"Fasa pembangunan awal. Organ dan sistem badan utama bayi sedang terbentuk. "
"Masa penting untuk penjagaan pranatal, asid folik, dan mengelakkan bahan "
"berbahaya. Morning sickness dan keletihan adalah perkara biasa."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:342
msgid "Second Trimester (Weeks 13-26)"
msgstr "Trimester Kedua (Minggu 13-26)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:344
msgid ""
"Often called the 'golden period.' Baby is growing rapidly, and you may start"
" feeling movement. Energy levels typically improve. Anatomy scan usually "
"performed around week 20."
msgstr ""
"Selalunya dipanggil 'tempoh emas.' Bayi sedang membesar dengan cepat, dan "
"anda mungkin mula merasakan pergerakan. Tahap tenaga biasanya bertambah "
"baik. Imbasan anatomi biasanya dilakukan sekitar minggu ke-20."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:348
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_weight_gain_calculator.html:462
msgid "Third Trimester (Weeks 27-40)"
msgstr "Trimester Ketiga (Minggu 27-40)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:350
msgid ""
"Final preparation phase. Baby is gaining weight and preparing for birth. "
"Regular checkups become more frequent. Braxton Hicks contractions may occur."
" Baby is considered full term at 37 weeks."
msgstr ""
"Fasa persediaan akhir. Bayi semakin bertambah berat dan bersedia untuk "
"kelahiran. Pemeriksaan berkala menjadi lebih kerap. Kontraksi Braxton Hicks "
"mungkin berlaku. Bayi dianggap cukup bulan pada 37 minggu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:360
msgid ""
"Choose your calculation method: From Last Menstrual Period (most common), "
"From Conception Date, or From Due Date"
msgstr ""
"Pilih kaedah pengiraan anda: Dari Tempoh Haid Terakhir (paling biasa), Dari "
"Tarikh Bersalin atau Dari Tarikh Tamat"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:361
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:383
msgid "Enter the required date information based on your selected method"
msgstr ""
"Masukkan maklumat tarikh yang diperlukan berdasarkan kaedah pilihan anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:362
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:384
msgid ""
"If using LMP method, enter your average cycle length (default is 28 days)"
msgstr ""
"Jika menggunakan kaedah LMP, masukkan purata panjang kitaran anda (lalai "
"ialah 28 hari)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:363
msgid "Click 'Calculate' to see comprehensive pregnancy tracking information"
msgstr ""
"Klik 'Kira' untuk melihat maklumat penjejakan kehamilan yang komprehensif"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:364
msgid ""
"Review your due date, weeks pregnant, trimester, milestones, and upcoming "
"appointments"
msgstr ""
"Semak tarikh akhir anda, minggu kehamilan, trimester, peristiwa penting dan "
"janji temu akan datang"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:376
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Estimated date of delivery (EDD). Calculated as 280 days (40 weeks) from the"
" first day of your last menstrual period. Only about 5%% of babies are born "
"exactly on their due date, but most are born within 2 weeks before or after."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran tarikh penghantaran (EDD). Dikira sebagai 280 hari (40 minggu) dari"
" hari pertama haid terakhir anda. Hanya kira-kira 5%% bayi dilahirkan tepat "
"pada tarikh akhir mereka, tetapi kebanyakannya dilahirkan dalam masa 2 "
"minggu sebelum atau selepas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"How many weeks you are into your pregnancy. Pregnancy is counted from the "
"first day of your last menstrual period, not from conception. This is why "
"you're considered 2 weeks pregnant at conception."
msgstr ""
"Berapa minggu anda memasuki kehamilan anda. Kehamilan dikira dari hari "
"pertama haid terakhir anda, bukan dari pembuahan. Inilah sebabnya mengapa "
"anda dianggap hamil 2 minggu semasa mengandung."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"Which trimester you're currently in. Each trimester has different "
"characteristics, milestones, and care requirements."
msgstr ""
"Trimester yang mana anda sedang berada. Setiap trimester mempunyai ciri, "
"pencapaian dan keperluan penjagaan yang berbeza."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:394
msgid ""
"Key developmental stages your baby reaches at different weeks. These "
"milestones show what's happening with your baby's growth and development."
msgstr ""
"Peringkat perkembangan utama yang dicapai bayi anda pada minggu yang "
"berbeza. Pencapaian ini menunjukkan apa yang berlaku dengan pertumbuhan dan "
"perkembangan bayi anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Typical prenatal care schedule. Regular checkups are essential for "
"monitoring your health and your baby's development. Your healthcare provider"
" may adjust this schedule based on your specific needs."
msgstr ""
"Jadual penjagaan pranatal yang biasa. Pemeriksaan berkala adalah penting "
"untuk memantau kesihatan anda dan perkembangan bayi anda. Penyedia penjagaan"
" kesihatan anda boleh melaraskan jadual ini berdasarkan keperluan khusus "
"anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:408
msgid "Important Pregnancy Milestones"
msgstr "Pencapaian Penting Kehamilan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:411
msgid "Week 4: Neural Tube Forms"
msgstr "Minggu 4: Bentuk Tiub Neural"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"Neural tube begins to form, which will become the brain and spinal cord. "
"Heart begins to beat. Critical time for folic acid intake."
msgstr ""
"Tiub neural mula terbentuk, yang akan menjadi otak dan saraf tunjang. "
"Jantung mula berdegup. Masa kritikal untuk pengambilan asid folik."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:417
msgid "Week 8: Major Organs Forming"
msgstr "Minggu 8: Pembentukan Organ Utama"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"All major organs are forming. Fingers and toes become visible. Baby is about"
" the size of a raspberry."
msgstr ""
"Semua organ utama sedang terbentuk. Jari tangan dan kaki menjadi kelihatan. "
"Bayi adalah kira-kira saiz raspberi."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:423
msgid "Week 20: Anatomy Scan"
msgstr "Minggu 20: Imbasan Anatomi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"Detailed ultrasound to check baby's anatomy. You may be able to find out the"
" baby's sex. Baby can swallow and hair begins to grow."
msgstr ""
"Ultrasound terperinci untuk memeriksa anatomi bayi. Anda mungkin boleh "
"mengetahui jantina bayi. Bayi boleh menelan dan rambut mula tumbuh."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:429
msgid "Week 24: Viability"
msgstr "Minggu 24: Daya maju"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:431
msgid ""
"Baby reaches viability - can potentially survive outside the womb with "
"medical assistance. Fingerprints are forming."
msgstr ""
"Bayi mencapai daya hidup - berpotensi bertahan di luar rahim dengan bantuan "
"perubatan. Cap jari sedang terbentuk."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:435
msgid "Week 37: Full Term"
msgstr "Minggu 37: Penggal Penuh"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:437
msgid ""
"Baby is considered full term. Lungs are mature. Baby is preparing for birth "
"and may move into head-down position."
msgstr ""
"Bayi dianggap cukup bulan. Paru-paru sudah matang. Bayi sedang bersiap untuk"
" kelahiran dan mungkin bergerak ke posisi kepala ke bawah."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:451
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Due dates are estimates. Only about 5%% of babies are born exactly on their "
"due date. Most babies are born between 38-42 weeks."
msgstr ""
"Tarikh tamat adalah anggaran. Hanya kira-kira 5%% bayi dilahirkan tepat pada"
" tarikh akhir mereka. Kebanyakan bayi dilahirkan antara 38-42 minggu."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:457
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:469
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is calculated from the first day of your last menstrual period "
"(LMP), not from conception. This is why you're considered 2 weeks pregnant "
"at conception."
msgstr ""
"Kehamilan dikira dari hari pertama haid terakhir anda (LMP), bukan dari "
"pembuahan. Inilah sebabnya mengapa anda dianggap hamil 2 minggu semasa "
"mengandung."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:463
msgid ""
"Regular prenatal care is essential. Follow your healthcare provider's "
"recommended schedule for checkups, tests, and screenings."
msgstr ""
"Penjagaan pranatal yang kerap adalah penting. Ikuti jadual disyorkan "
"pembekal penjagaan kesihatan anda untuk pemeriksaan, ujian dan pemeriksaan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:469
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:481
msgid ""
"This calculator is for informational purposes only and should not replace "
"professional medical advice. Always consult with qualified healthcare "
"providers (OB/GYN, midwife, or family doctor) for pregnancy care, concerns, "
"or questions."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator ini adalah untuk tujuan maklumat sahaja dan tidak boleh "
"menggantikan nasihat perubatan profesional. Sentiasa berunding dengan "
"penyedia penjagaan kesihatan yang berkelayakan (OB/GYN, bidan atau doktor "
"keluarga) untuk penjagaan kehamilan, kebimbangan atau soalan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:475
msgid ""
"If you experience any concerning symptoms (bleeding, severe pain, decreased "
"fetal movement after 28 weeks, etc.), contact your healthcare provider "
"immediately."
msgstr ""
"Jika anda mengalami sebarang gejala (pendarahan, sakit teruk, pergerakan "
"janin menurun selepas 28 minggu, dsb.), hubungi pembekal penjagaan kesihatan"
" anda dengan segera."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:701
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_calculator.html:720
msgid "Week"
msgstr "Minggu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:5
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:14
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:23
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:48
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/views/index.py:49
msgid "Pregnancy Conception Calculator"
msgstr "Kalkulator Konsep Kehamilan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your conception date and pregnancy timeline. Track fertile window,"
" ovulation, and implantation dates."
msgstr ""
"Kira tarikh konsep dan garis masa kehamilan anda. Jejaki tetingkap subur, "
"ovulasi dan tarikh implantasi."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"pregnancy conception calculator, conception date, fertile window, ovulation "
"calculator, implantation"
msgstr ""
"kalkulator konsep kehamilan, tarikh konsep, tingkap subur, kalkulator "
"ovulasi, implantasi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate your conception date and track pregnancy timeline."
msgstr "Kira tarikh konsep anda dan jejaki garis masa kehamilan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate conception date and pregnancy timeline"
msgstr "Kira tarikh konsep dan garis masa kehamilan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your conception date and track important pregnancy milestones "
"including fertile window, ovulation, and implantation dates."
msgstr ""
"Kira tarikh konsep anda dan jejaki peristiwa penting kehamilan termasuk "
"tarikh subur, ovulasi dan tarikh implantasi."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:65
msgid "Calculate Conception"
msgstr "Kira Konsep"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:96
msgid "Estimated date of delivery"
msgstr "Anggaran tarikh penghantaran"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:120
msgid "Date when conception occurred"
msgstr "Tarikh kehamilan berlaku"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:164
msgid ""
"Enter your information using any calculation method, then click Calculate to"
" see your conception date, fertile window, ovulation, implantation dates, "
"and comprehensive pregnancy timeline."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan maklumat anda menggunakan sebarang kaedah pengiraan, kemudian klik "
"Kira untuk melihat tarikh konsep anda, tetingkap subur, ovulasi, tarikh "
"implantasi dan garis masa kehamilan yang komprehensif."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:193
msgid "Weeks Since Conception"
msgstr "Minggu Sejak Konsepsi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:230
msgid "Fertile Window & Ovulation"
msgstr "Tingkap Subur & Ovulasi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:243
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:408
msgid "Implantation Window"
msgstr "Tingkap Implantasi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:246
msgid "Implantation Start"
msgstr "Permulaan Implantasi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:250
msgid "Implantation End"
msgstr "Tamat Implantasi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:278
msgid "Weeks Comparison"
msgstr "Perbandingan Minggu"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:307
msgid "Conception Timeline"
msgstr "Garis Masa Konsepsi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"Conception occurs when a sperm fertilizes an egg, typically happening during"
" ovulation. This is the moment when pregnancy begins. The fertilized egg "
"then travels to the uterus and implants in the uterine lining, usually 6-12 "
"days after conception."
msgstr ""
"Konsepsi berlaku apabila sperma menyuburkan telur, biasanya berlaku semasa "
"ovulasi. Ini adalah saat apabila kehamilan bermula. Telur yang disenyawakan "
"kemudian bergerak ke rahim dan implan dalam lapisan rahim, biasanya 6-12 "
"hari selepas pembuahan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"Understanding your conception date helps you track your pregnancy timeline "
"more accurately and provides insight into when important milestones occur."
msgstr ""
"Memahami tarikh konsep anda membantu anda menjejaki garis masa kehamilan "
"anda dengan lebih tepat dan memberikan gambaran tentang apabila peristiwa "
"penting berlaku."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:349
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/factor_calculator.html:510
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/prime_factorization_calculator.html:267
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/probability_calculator.html:365
msgid "Key Concepts"
msgstr "Konsep Utama"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:354
msgid ""
"The date when the sperm fertilized the egg. This typically occurs during "
"ovulation, approximately 14 days after the start of your last menstrual "
"period (for a 28-day cycle)."
msgstr ""
"Tarikh apabila sperma menyenyawakan telur. Ini biasanya berlaku semasa "
"ovulasi, kira-kira 14 hari selepas permulaan haid terakhir anda (untuk "
"kitaran 28 hari)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:360
msgid ""
"The 6-7 day period when conception is most likely. Includes 5 days before "
"ovulation, the day of ovulation, and 1 day after. Sperm can survive up to 5 "
"days in the female reproductive tract."
msgstr ""
"Tempoh 6-7 hari apabila pembuahan berkemungkinan besar. Termasuk 5 hari "
"sebelum ovulasi, hari ovulasi, dan 1 hari selepasnya. Sperma boleh bertahan "
"sehingga 5 hari dalam saluran pembiakan wanita."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:366
msgid ""
"The release of a mature egg from the ovary. This is your most fertile day. "
"The egg survives for 12-24 hours after release, so timing intercourse around"
" ovulation is crucial for conception."
msgstr ""
"Pembebasan telur matang dari ovari. Ini adalah hari paling subur anda. Telur"
" bertahan selama 12-24 jam selepas dilepaskan, jadi masa hubungan intim "
"sekitar ovulasi adalah penting untuk pembuahan."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:370
msgid "Implantation"
msgstr "Implantasi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:372
msgid ""
"When the fertilized egg attaches to the uterine lining. This typically "
"occurs 6-12 days after conception. Implantation bleeding (light spotting) "
"may occur but is not always present."
msgstr ""
"Apabila telur yang disenyawakan melekat pada lapisan rahim. Ini biasanya "
"berlaku 6-12 hari selepas pembuahan. Pendarahan implantasi (bintik cahaya) "
"mungkin berlaku tetapi tidak selalu ada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"Choose your calculation method: From Due Date, From Last Menstrual Period, "
"or From Conception Date"
msgstr ""
"Pilih kaedah pengiraan anda: Dari Tarikh Tamat, Dari Tempoh Haid Terakhir, "
"atau Dari Tarikh Pembuahan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:385
msgid ""
"Click 'Calculate' to see your conception date and comprehensive timeline"
msgstr ""
"Klik 'Kira' untuk melihat tarikh konsep anda dan garis masa yang "
"komprehensif"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:386
msgid ""
"Review fertile window, ovulation date, implantation window, and pregnancy "
"status"
msgstr ""
"Semak tingkap subur, tarikh ovulasi, tingkap implantasi, dan status "
"kehamilan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:387
msgid "Use the charts to visualize your pregnancy progress and timeline"
msgstr ""
"Gunakan carta untuk menggambarkan perkembangan kehamilan dan garis masa anda"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:398
msgid ""
"The estimated date when conception occurred. This is calculated based on "
"your due date, LMP, or known conception date. Conception typically occurs "
"during ovulation, approximately 14 days after the start of your last period."
msgstr ""
"Anggaran tarikh kehamilan berlaku. Ini dikira berdasarkan tarikh akhir anda,"
" LMP atau tarikh konsep yang diketahui. Konsepsi biasanya berlaku semasa "
"ovulasi, kira-kira 14 hari selepas permulaan haid terakhir anda."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:404
msgid ""
"The 6-7 day period when conception was most likely. This includes 5 days "
"before ovulation, the day of ovulation, and 1 day after. Having intercourse "
"during this window maximizes chances of conception."
msgstr ""
"Tempoh 6-7 hari apabila pembuahan berkemungkinan besar. Ini termasuk 5 hari "
"sebelum ovulasi, hari ovulasi, dan 1 hari selepasnya. Melakukan persetubuhan"
" semasa tingkap ini memaksimumkan peluang untuk hamil."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:410
msgid ""
"The period when the fertilized egg typically implants in the uterine lining "
"(6-12 days after conception). Some women may experience light spotting "
"during this time, known as implantation bleeding."
msgstr ""
"Tempoh apabila telur yang disenyawakan biasanya implan dalam lapisan rahim "
"(6-12 hari selepas pembuahan). Sesetengah wanita mungkin mengalami tompok "
"ringan pada masa ini, yang dikenali sebagai pendarahan implantasi."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:414
msgid "Weeks Pregnant vs Weeks Since Conception"
msgstr "Minggu Hamil vs Minggu Sejak Mengandung"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:416
msgid ""
"Pregnancy is counted from the first day of your last menstrual period (LMP),"
" not from conception. This is why you're considered 2 weeks pregnant at "
"conception. Weeks since conception is the actual time since fertilization "
"occurred."
msgstr ""
"Kehamilan dikira dari hari pertama haid terakhir anda (LMP), bukan dari "
"pembuahan. Inilah sebabnya mengapa anda dianggap hamil 2 minggu semasa "
"mengandung. Minggu sejak pembuahan adalah masa sebenar sejak persenyawaan "
"berlaku."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:429
msgid "Last Menstrual Period (LMP) - Day 1 of pregnancy"
msgstr "Tempoh Haid Terakhir (LMP) - Hari 1 kehamilan"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:433
msgid "Fertile Window Begins - 5 days before ovulation"
msgstr "Tingkap Subur Bermula - 5 hari sebelum ovulasi"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:437
msgid "Ovulation - Release of mature egg (most fertile day)"
msgstr "Ovulasi - Pembebasan telur matang (hari paling subur)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:441
msgid "Conception - Sperm fertilizes egg (typically on ovulation day)"
msgstr "Konsepsi - Sperma menyuburkan telur (biasanya pada hari ovulasi)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:445
msgid ""
"Implantation - Fertilized egg attaches to uterus (6-12 days after "
"conception)"
msgstr ""
"Implantasi - Telur yang telah disenyawakan melekat pada rahim (6-12 hari "
"selepas pembuahan)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:449
msgid "Due Date - Approximately 266 days from conception or 280 days from LMP"
msgstr ""
"Tarikh Akhir - Kira-kira 266 hari dari pembuahan atau 280 hari dari LMP"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:463
msgid ""
"Conception dates are estimates. The exact moment of conception cannot be "
"determined with certainty, but it typically occurs during the fertile "
"window, most likely on or near the day of ovulation."
msgstr ""
"Tarikh konsep adalah anggaran. Saat pembuahan yang tepat tidak dapat "
"ditentukan dengan pasti, tetapi ia biasanya berlaku semasa tingkap subur, "
"kemungkinan besar pada atau berhampiran hari ovulasi."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/pregnancy_conception_calculator.html:475
msgid ""
"Implantation bleeding is light spotting that may occur 6-12 days after "
"conception. Not all women experience this, and it's different from menstrual"
" bleeding."
msgstr ""
"Pendarahan implantasi adalah tompok ringan yang mungkin berlaku 6-12 hari "
"selepas pembuahan. Tidak semua wanita mengalami ini, dan ia berbeza dengan "
"pendarahan haid."

