msgid "What is a binary calculator?"
msgstr "Apakah kalkulator binari?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:117
msgid ""
"A binary calculator is a tool that performs arithmetic and bitwise "
"operations on binary numbers, and converts between different number bases "
"including binary, decimal, hexadecimal, and octal."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator binari ialah alat yang menjalankan operasi aritmetik dan bitwise "
"pada nombor binari, dan menukar antara asas nombor yang berbeza termasuk "
"perduaan, perpuluhan, perenambelasan dan perlapanan."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:122
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:444
msgid "How do I convert binary to decimal?"
msgstr "Bagaimanakah cara menukar binari kepada perpuluhan?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:125
msgid ""
"Enter your binary number, select Conversion operation, and the calculator "
"will display the decimal equivalent along with hexadecimal and octal "
"conversions."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan nombor perduaan anda, pilih Operasi penukaran, dan kalkulator akan "
"memaparkan persamaan perpuluhan bersama-sama dengan penukaran heksadesimal "
"dan perlapanan."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:130
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:450
msgid "What are bitwise operations?"
msgstr "Apakah operasi bitwise?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:133
msgid ""
"Bitwise operations perform logical operations on individual bits. Common "
"operations include AND (&), OR (|), XOR (^), and NOT (~)."
msgstr ""
"Operasi bitwise melaksanakan operasi logik pada bit individu. Operasi biasa "
"termasuk AND (&), OR (|), XOR (^), dan NOT (~)."

