#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/greatest_common_factor_calculator.html:275
msgid "What is GCD?"
msgstr "Apakah GCD?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/greatest_common_factor_calculator.html:277
msgid ""
"GCD (Greatest Common Divisor) or GCF (Greatest Common Factor) is the largest"
" positive integer that divides each of the given numbers without leaving a "
"remainder."
msgstr ""
"GCD (Pembahagi Sepunya Terbesar) atau GCF (Faktor Sepunya Terhebat) ialah "
"integer positif terbesar yang membahagi setiap nombor yang diberi tanpa "
"meninggalkan baki."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/greatest_common_factor_calculator.html:280
msgid ""
"For example, GCD of 24 and 36 is 12, because 12 is the largest number that "
"divides both 24 and 36 evenly."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai contoh, GCD bagi 24 dan 36 ialah 12, kerana 12 ialah nombor terbesar"
" yang membahagikan kedua-dua 24 dan 36 sama rata."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/greatest_common_factor_calculator.html:285
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:261
msgid "What is LCM?"
msgstr "Apakah LCM?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/greatest_common_factor_calculator.html:287
msgid ""
"LCM (Least Common Multiple) is the smallest positive integer that is a "
"multiple of each of the given numbers."
msgstr ""
"LCM (Least Common Multiple) ialah integer positif terkecil yang merupakan "
"gandaan bagi setiap nombor yang diberikan."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/greatest_common_factor_calculator.html:290
msgid ""
"For example, LCM of 24 and 36 is 72, because 72 is the smallest number that "
"is divisible by both 24 and 36."
msgstr ""
"Sebagai contoh, KPK bagi 24 dan 36 ialah 72, kerana 72 ialah nombor terkecil"
" yang boleh dibahagi dengan kedua-dua 24 dan 36."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/greatest_common_factor_calculator.html:297
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/least_common_multiple_calculator.html:273
msgid "Enter two or more positive integers (separated by commas or new lines)"
msgstr ""
