#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:29
msgid ""
"Bandwidth Calculator - Calculate Data Transfer Time, Required Bandwidth & "
"File Size"
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator Lebar Jalur - Kira Masa Pemindahan Data, Lebar Jalur Diperlukan &"
" Saiz Fail"

