"sebenar, perbandingan sambungan, pengiraan kos dan cadangan lebar jalur. "
"Sesuai untuk perancangan rangkaian dan anggaran masa muat turun/muat naik."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:6
msgid ""
"bandwidth calculator, data transfer time, download time, upload time, "
