#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:8
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:12
msgid ""
"Bandwidth Calculator - Calculate Data Transfer Time & Required Bandwidth"
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator Lebar Jalur - Kira Masa Pemindahan Data & Lebar Jalur Diperlukan"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:9
msgid ""
"Calculate data transfer time, required bandwidth, and file sizes. Free "
"online bandwidth calculator with real-world speed estimates and connection "
"comparisons."
msgstr ""
"Kira masa pemindahan data, lebar jalur yang diperlukan dan saiz fail. "
"Kalkulator lebar jalur dalam talian percuma dengan anggaran kelajuan dunia "
"sebenar dan perbandingan sambungan."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bandwidth_calculator.html:13
msgid ""
"Calculate data transfer time and required bandwidth. Free online calculator."
msgstr ""
