#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:509
msgid "What is Bra Size?"
msgstr "Apakah Saiz Bra?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:511
msgid ""
"Bra size consists of two components: the band size (number) and the cup size"
" (letter). The band size is the measurement around your ribcage, typically "
"ranging from 28 to 50. The cup size represents the difference between your "
"bust and band measurements, ranging from AA to N."
msgstr ""
"Saiz bra terdiri daripada dua komponen: saiz jalur (nombor) dan saiz cawan "
"(huruf). Saiz jalur ialah ukuran di sekeliling tulang rusuk anda, biasanya "
"antara 28 hingga 50. Saiz cawan mewakili perbezaan antara ukuran payudara "
"dan jalur anda, antara AA hingga N."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:514
msgid "Bra Size = Band Size + Cup Size"
msgstr "Saiz Bra = Saiz Band + Saiz Cawan"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:517
msgid ""
"Understanding your correct bra size is essential for comfort, support, and "
"proper fit. This calculator helps you determine your bra size accurately "
"using standard measurement methods."
msgstr ""
"Memahami saiz coli anda yang betul adalah penting untuk keselesaan, sokongan"
" dan kesesuaian yang betul. Kalkulator ini membantu anda menentukan saiz "
"coli anda dengan tepat menggunakan kaedah pengukuran standard."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:525
msgid ""
"Select the calculation type: Calculate Bra Size, Size Conversion, or Sister "
"Sizes."
msgstr "Pilih jenis pengiraan: Kira Saiz Bra, Penukaran Saiz atau Saiz Kakak."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:526
msgid ""
"Enter your measurements (underbust and bust) or bra size based on your "
"selected calculation type."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan ukuran anda (underbust dan bust) atau saiz coli berdasarkan jenis "
"pengiraan yang anda pilih."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:527
msgid "Select your preferred sizing system (US, UK, EU, FR, or AU)."
msgstr "Pilih sistem saiz pilihan anda (AS, UK, EU, FR atau AU)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:529
msgid ""
"Review the detailed breakdown, size comparisons, and step-by-step solution."
msgstr ""
"Semak pecahan terperinci, perbandingan saiz dan penyelesaian langkah demi "
"langkah."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:540
msgid ""
"Calculate your bra size from underbust and bust measurements. Get your size "
"in all sizing systems, sister sizes, and detailed calculations."
msgstr ""
"Kira saiz coli anda daripada ukuran underbust dan payudara. Dapatkan saiz "
"anda dalam semua sistem saiz, saiz kakak dan pengiraan terperinci."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:546
msgid ""
"Convert bra sizes between different sizing systems (US, UK, EU, FR, AU). "
"Useful when shopping from international brands."
msgstr ""
"Tukar saiz coli antara sistem saiz yang berbeza (AS, UK, EU, FR, AU). "
"Berguna apabila membeli-belah dari jenama antarabangsa."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:552
msgid ""
"Find sister sizes (alternative sizes with the same cup volume). Useful when "
