msgstr "Ukur panjang, lebar dan tinggi bilik anda dalam kaki atau meter."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:76
msgid "Select Room Type"
msgstr "Pilih Jenis Bilik"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:77
msgid ""
"Choose the room type (bedroom, living room, kitchen, etc.) as different "
"rooms have different BTU requirements per square foot."
msgstr ""
"Pilih jenis bilik (bilik tidur, ruang tamu, dapur, dll.) kerana bilik yang "
"berbeza mempunyai keperluan BTU yang berbeza bagi setiap kaki persegi."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:81
msgid "Determine Insulation Quality"
msgstr "Tentukan Kualiti Penebat"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:82
msgid ""
"Select the insulation quality of your room (excellent, good, average, poor, "
"or none)."
msgstr ""
"Pilih kualiti penebat bilik anda (cemerlang, baik, sederhana, buruk atau "
"tiada)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:86
msgid "Select Climate Zone"
msgstr "Pilih Zon Iklim"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:87
msgid "Choose your climate zone based on average temperatures in your area."
msgstr "Pilih zon iklim anda berdasarkan purata suhu di kawasan anda."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:91
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:449
msgid "Calculate BTU"
msgstr "Kira BTU"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:92
msgid ""
"The calculator will compute the total BTU required based on area, room type,"
" insulation, and climate zone."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator akan mengira jumlah BTU yang diperlukan berdasarkan kawasan, "
"jenis bilik, penebat dan zon iklim."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:105
msgid "What is BTU and why is it important?"
msgstr "Apakah BTU dan mengapa ia penting?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:108
msgid ""
"BTU (British Thermal Unit) is a unit of energy used to measure heating and "
"cooling capacity. It represents the amount of energy needed to raise the "
"temperature of one pound of water by one degree Fahrenheit. BTU is important"
" for sizing HVAC systems correctly."
msgstr ""
"BTU (British Thermal Unit) ialah unit tenaga yang digunakan untuk mengukur "
"kapasiti pemanasan dan penyejukan. Ia mewakili jumlah tenaga yang diperlukan"
" untuk menaikkan suhu satu paun air sebanyak satu darjah Fahrenheit. BTU "
"adalah penting untuk mensaiz sistem HVAC dengan betul."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:113
msgid "How many BTU per square foot do I need?"
msgstr "Berapa banyak BTU bagi setiap kaki persegi yang saya perlukan?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:116
msgid ""
"The standard rule is approximately 20 BTU per square foot for heating. "
"However, this varies based on room type (bedroom: 20, kitchen: 30, bathroom:"
" 15), insulation quality, and climate zone. Our calculator accounts for all "
"these factors."
msgstr ""
"Peraturan standard ialah kira-kira 20 BTU setiap kaki persegi untuk "
"pemanasan. Walau bagaimanapun, ini berbeza-beza berdasarkan jenis bilik "
"(bilik tidur: 20, dapur: 30, bilik mandi: 15), kualiti penebat dan zon "
"iklim. Kalkulator kami mengambil kira semua faktor ini."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:121
msgid "How do I convert BTU to other energy units?"
msgstr "Bagaimanakah saya menukar BTU kepada unit tenaga lain?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:124
msgid ""
"You can convert BTU to kWh (1 BTU = 0.000293071 kWh), Joules (1 BTU = "
"1055.06 J), Calories (1 BTU = 252.164 cal), or Foot-Pounds (1 BTU = 778.169 "
"ft-lb). Use our unit conversion mode for accurate conversions."
msgstr ""
"Anda boleh menukar BTU kepada kWj (1 BTU = 0.000293071 kWj), Joule (1 BTU = "
"1055.06 J), Kalori (1 BTU = 252.164 kal) atau Foot-Pounds (1 BTU = 778.169 "
"ft-lb). Gunakan mod penukaran unit kami untuk penukaran yang tepat."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:129
msgid "What factors affect BTU requirements?"
msgstr "Apakah faktor yang mempengaruhi keperluan BTU?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/btu_calculator.html:132
msgid ""
"BTU requirements are affected by room size, room type, insulation quality, "
"climate zone, number of windows, number of occupants, and heat-generating "
"appliances. Our calculator considers all these factors."
msgstr ""
"Keperluan BTU dipengaruhi oleh saiz bilik, jenis bilik, kualiti penebat, zon"
" iklim, bilangan tingkap, bilangan penghuni dan peralatan penjana haba. "
"Kalkulator kami mengambil kira semua faktor ini."

