msgstr "Penukaran:"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:472
msgid ""
"MPG (Miles Per Gallon) is the US standard for measuring fuel efficiency, "
"representing how many miles a vehicle can travel on one gallon of fuel. "
"L/100km (Liters Per 100 Kilometers) is the metric standard, representing how"
" many liters of fuel are needed to travel 100 kilometers. Lower L/100km "
"values indicate better fuel efficiency."
msgstr ""
"MPG (Miles Per Gallon) ialah piawaian AS untuk mengukur kecekapan bahan api,"
" mewakili berapa batu yang boleh dilalui oleh kenderaan dengan satu gelen "
"bahan api. L/100km (Liter Per 100 Kilometer) ialah piawaian metrik, mewakili"
" berapa liter bahan api yang diperlukan untuk menempuh jarak 100 kilometer. "
"Nilai L/100km yang lebih rendah menunjukkan kecekapan bahan api yang lebih "
"baik."

