msgstr ""
"Kalkulator secara automatik mengendalikan penukaran unit antara sistem "
"imperial dan metrik."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/fuel_cost_calculator.html:539
msgid ""
"MPG and L/100km are inversely related - higher MPG means lower L/100km."
msgstr ""
"MPG dan L/100km berkait songsang - MPG yang lebih tinggi bermakna L/100km "
