msgstr ""
"Semua nilai input mestilah bukan negatif (kecuali keuntungan yang boleh "
"negatif)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:429
msgid ""
"Previous GDP and Real GDP cannot be zero for growth rate and deflator "
