msgstr ""
"Kalkulator secara automatik mengendalikan penukaran unit antara berjuta, "
"berbilion dan trilion."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Expenditure and income approaches should yield the same GDP value in theory."
msgstr ""
"Pendekatan perbelanjaan dan pendapatan harus menghasilkan nilai KDNK yang "
"sama secara teori."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:433
msgid "GDP deflator of 100 means no inflation; above 100 indicates inflation."
msgstr ""
"Pendeflator KDNK sebanyak 100 bermakna tiada inflasi; melebihi 100 "
