#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:473
msgid "What is Gravel Calculator?"
msgstr "Apakah Kalkulator Kerikil?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:475
msgid ""
"The Gravel Calculator is a comprehensive tool for calculating gravel volume,"
" weight, cost, and coverage for various project shapes. It helps you "
"determine how much gravel you need for rectangular driveways, circular "
"patios, triangular areas, and more. This calculator is essential for "
"landscaping, construction, and DIY projects."
msgstr ""
"Kalkulator Kerikil ialah alat yang komprehensif untuk mengira isipadu "
"kerikil, berat, kos dan liputan untuk pelbagai bentuk projek. Ia membantu "
"anda menentukan jumlah kerikil yang anda perlukan untuk jalan masuk segi "
"empat tepat, teres bulat, kawasan segi tiga dan banyak lagi. Kalkulator ini "
"penting untuk landskap, pembinaan dan projek DIY."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:482
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Rectangular Area, Circular "
"Area, Triangular Area, Weight, Cost, Coverage, or Unit Conversion)."
msgstr ""
"Pilih jenis pengiraan daripada menu lungsur (Kawasan Segi Empat, Luas "
"Pekeliling, Luas Segi Tiga, Berat, Kos, Liputan atau Penukaran Unit)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:483
msgid ""
"Enter the required dimensions (length, width, depth, diameter, etc.) with "
"appropriate units."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan dimensi yang diperlukan (panjang, lebar, kedalaman, diameter, dll.)"
" dengan unit yang sesuai."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:484
msgid ""
"Select your preferred result unit (cubic yards, cubic feet, cubic meters, "
"tons, etc.)."
msgstr ""
"Pilih unit hasil pilihan anda (ela padu, kaki padu, meter padu, tan, dsb.)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:495
msgid ""
"Calculate gravel volume for rectangular areas like driveways, walkways, and "
"patios. Formula: Volume = Length × Width × Depth."
msgstr ""
"Kira isipadu batu kelikir untuk kawasan segi empat tepat seperti jalan "
"masuk, laluan pejalan kaki dan laman dalam. Formula: Isipadu = Panjang × "
"Lebar × Kedalaman."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:499
msgid ""
"Calculate gravel volume for circular areas like round patios and fire pits. "
"Formula: Volume = π × (Diameter/2)² × Depth."
msgstr ""
"Kira isipadu batu kelikir untuk kawasan bulat seperti teres bulat dan lubang"
" api. Formula: Isipadu = π × (Diameter/2)² × Kedalaman."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:503
msgid ""
"Calculate gravel volume for triangular areas. Formula: Volume = (1/2) × Base"
" × Height × Depth."
msgstr ""
"Kira isipadu batu kelikir untuk kawasan segi tiga. Formula: Isipadu = (1/2) "
"× Tapak × Tinggi × Kedalaman."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:507
msgid ""
"Calculate gravel weight from volume. Formula: Weight = Volume × Density. "
"Default density: 105 lbs/ft³."
msgstr ""
"Kira berat kerikil daripada isipadu. Formula: Berat = Isipadu × Ketumpatan. "
"Ketumpatan lalai: 105 lbs/ft³."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:511
msgid ""
"Calculate total cost of gravel. Formula: Total Cost = Volume × Price per "
"Unit."
msgstr ""
"Kira jumlah kos kerikil. Formula: Jumlah Kos = Isipadu × Harga seunit."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gravel_calculator.html:515
msgid ""
"Calculate coverage area from volume and depth. Formula: Area = Volume / "
"Depth."
msgstr ""
"Kira kawasan liputan daripada isipadu dan kedalaman. Formula: Luas = Isipadu"
" / Kedalaman."

