#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/voltage_drop_calculator.html:400
msgid ""
"Power factor is the ratio of real power to apparent power. For resistive "
"loads (heaters, incandescent lights), power factor is 1.0. For inductive "
"loads (motors, transformers), power factor is typically 0.7-0.9."
msgstr ""
"Faktor kuasa ialah nisbah kuasa sebenar kepada kuasa ketara. Untuk beban "
"rintangan (pemanas, lampu pijar), faktor kuasa ialah 1.0. Untuk beban "
"induktif (motor, transformer), faktor kuasa biasanya 0.7-0.9."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/voltage_drop_calculator.html:406
msgid "Voltage drop increases with wire length"
msgstr "Kejatuhan voltan meningkat dengan panjang wayar"

