#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:69
msgid ""
"Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device (computer, "
"tablet, or mobile phone) when you visit a website. They are widely used to "
"make websites work more efficiently, as well as to provide information to "
"the website owners."
msgstr ""
"Kuki ialah fail teks kecil yang disimpan pada peranti anda (komputer, tablet"
" atau telefon mudah alih) apabila anda melawat tapak web. Ia digunakan "
"secara meluas untuk menjadikan tapak web berfungsi dengan lebih cekap, serta"
" memberikan maklumat kepada pemilik laman web."

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:73
msgid ""
"Calculator Drive uses cookies to enhance your experience, understand how you"
" use our Site, and improve our services. This Cookie Policy explains how we "
"use cookies and similar tracking technologies."
msgstr ""
"Pemacu Kalkulator menggunakan kuki untuk meningkatkan pengalaman anda, "
"memahami cara anda menggunakan Tapak kami dan menambah baik perkhidmatan "
"kami. Dasar Kuki ini menerangkan cara kami menggunakan kuki dan teknologi "
"penjejakan yang serupa."

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:87
msgid "Types of Cookies We Use"
msgstr "Jenis Kuki Yang Kami Gunakan"

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:95
msgid "Essential Cookies"
msgstr "Kuki Penting"

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:98
msgid ""
"These cookies are necessary for the Site to function properly. They enable "
"basic functionality such as page navigation, security features, and access "
"to secure areas of the Site. Without these cookies, the Site may not work "
"properly."
msgstr ""
"Kuki ini diperlukan untuk Tapak berfungsi dengan baik. Ia membolehkan "
"kefungsian asas seperti navigasi halaman, ciri keselamatan dan akses kepada "
"kawasan selamat di Tapak. Tanpa kuki ini, Tapak mungkin tidak berfungsi "
"dengan baik."

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:107
msgid "Performance Cookies"
msgstr "Kuki Prestasi"

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:110
msgid ""
"These cookies collect information about how visitors use the Site, such as "
"which pages are visited, whether an error occurred, and how long a visitor "
"stayed on a page. These cookies do not collect information that identifies a"
" visitor personally."
msgstr ""
"Kuki ini mengumpul maklumat tentang cara pelawat menggunakan Tapak, seperti "
"halaman mana yang dilawati, sama ada ralat berlaku dan berapa lama pelawat "
"tinggal di halaman. Kuki ini tidak mengumpul maklumat yang mengenal pasti "
"pelawat secara peribadi."

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:119
msgid "Preference Cookies"
msgstr "Kuki Keutamaan"

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:122
msgid ""
"These cookies remember choices you make to provide a more personalized "
"experience, such as your language preference or settings."
msgstr ""
"Kuki ini mengingati pilihan yang anda buat untuk memberikan pengalaman yang "
"lebih diperibadikan, seperti pilihan bahasa atau tetapan anda."

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:131
msgid "Marketing Cookies"
msgstr "Kuki Pemasaran"

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:134
msgid ""
"These cookies are used to track visitors across websites for the purpose of "
"displaying relevant advertisements on other sites. We use these only with "
"your consent."
msgstr ""
"Kuki ini digunakan untuk menjejaki pelawat merentas tapak web untuk tujuan "
"memaparkan iklan yang berkaitan di tapak lain. Kami menggunakan ini hanya "
"dengan persetujuan anda."

#: core/templates/core/cookie_policy.html:151
msgid ""
"We may allow third-party service providers to place cookies on your device. "
"These may include:"
